WEBVTT

00:00:38.680 --> 00:00:41.210
这是个简单的故事
This is a simple story...

00:00:41.470 --> 00:00:43.880
但不易说
but not an easy one to tell.

00:00:44.310 --> 00:00:46.180
像寓言  有悲有喜
Like a fable, there is sorrow...

00:00:46.230 --> 00:00:49.970
也像寓言  让人不可思议
and, like a fable, it is full of wonder and happiness.

00:00:53.900 --> 00:00:54.850
1939年  意大利中部

00:00:54.010 --> 00:00:57.010
我唱我所见  没有什么能逃过我的双眼
I sing what I see. Nothing gets by me.

00:00:57.090 --> 00:00:58.590
我对混乱说  我在这儿
"Here I am," said I to chaos.

00:00:58.910 --> 00:01:01.280
我是你的奴隶  混沌赞  好
"I am your slave!" And he: "Good."

00:01:01.450 --> 00:01:03.110
我说  用不着你赞好
"For what?" said I.

00:01:03.580 --> 00:01:08.160
我终于自由  比起我的喜悦...
Free in the end, I am! What good is a caress when bliss...

00:01:08.420 --> 00:01:10.040
你的赞好  算是什么
this man came to possess?

00:01:10.260 --> 00:01:12.000
我已经准备好
Here I am, ready.

00:01:12.340 --> 00:01:14.800
像火车般飞驰  然而刹掣不管用
The trains are gone, the brakes are gone.

00:01:15.180 --> 00:01:18.510
我再也无法抵抗  迷人的酒神啊  带上我
And I can resist no more. Go, sweet Bacchus, take me.

00:01:18.640 --> 00:01:21.760
刹闸不管用  刹闸不管用
The brakes are gone! The brakes are gone!

00:01:22.020 --> 00:01:23.020
我听到了
I heard you.

00:01:23.100 --> 00:01:26.140
-刹闸失灵了  -踩下去
- No, they're really gone! - Hit the brakes!

00:01:26.190 --> 00:01:27.390
我还以为你在念诗
Weren't you reciting a poem?

00:01:29.400 --> 00:01:30.820
汽车刹不住
It doesn't work!

00:01:36.040 --> 00:01:36.990
刹车
Brake!

00:01:37.210 --> 00:01:41.620
我们死定了  树林
We're going to die! The woods!

00:01:46.430 --> 00:01:48.330
刹车
Brake!

00:01:53.560 --> 00:01:54.970
国王驾到
The king is coming!

00:01:55.480 --> 00:01:57.520
国王来了
There he is!

00:01:59.190 --> 00:02:01.940
前面人潮涌动  直驶
It's full of people down there. Straight.

00:02:01.990 --> 00:02:03.560
刹闸没了
We have no brakes!

00:02:03.740 --> 00:02:08.820
我们没有刹闸  挪开
We have no brakes! Move!

00:02:24.890 --> 00:02:26.090
美丽人生
LIFE IS BEAUTIFUL

00:02:34.230 --> 00:02:36.110
出去走动走动
Go for a walk.

00:02:37.070 --> 00:02:38.730
否则明天也到不了
Otherwise, we'll get there tomorrow.

00:02:39.320 --> 00:02:40.650
我找到螺丝了
I found the screw.

00:02:42.410 --> 00:02:43.740
你现在需要什么
Now what do you need?

00:02:44.500 --> 00:02:46.740
没别的  只要让我清静10分钟
Nothing. I need ten minutes alone.

00:02:47.540 --> 00:02:50.030
行  我走开
All right, I’ll leave you alone.

00:02:50.380 --> 00:02:51.840
要刚才的螺丝吗
Do you want the screw from before?

00:02:52.590 --> 00:02:55.160
不要  只要你走开
No, I just want to be alone.

00:03:06.400 --> 00:03:08.470
如果找到了颗螺丝  我应该扔掉吗
Do I toss out the screw if I find it?

00:03:08.220 --> 00:03:11.440
就让我一个人待10分钟吧
I need ten minutes alone.

00:03:13.450 --> 00:03:15.360
那我去洗洗手
I'm washing my hands.

00:03:22.540 --> 00:03:26.160
小姑娘  你好
Pretty girl! How's it going?

00:03:26.510 --> 00:03:27.460
在干什么
What are you doing?

00:03:28.340 --> 00:03:30.380
那些东西是你妈妈的吗
Did your mom put this stuff here?

00:03:30.640 --> 00:03:31.800
不  是女房东的
No, the landlady did.

00:03:32.010 --> 00:03:35.510
在摆卖吗  好极了
Is it a market? It's beautiful.

00:03:35.680 --> 00:03:37.760
这个多少钱  你多大了
How much is it? How old are you?

00:03:38.090 --> 00:03:39.590
看来是我问的太多了  你叫什么
I ask too many questions. What's your name?

00:03:39.760 --> 00:03:40.800
Eleonora
Eleonora.

00:03:41.780 --> 00:03:43.850
幸会  我是Guido王子
Nice to meet you. I'm Prince Guido.

00:03:44.030 --> 00:03:45.110
你是王子
Prince?

00:03:45.400 --> 00:03:47.200
我真的是王子哦
I'm a prince, I am.

00:03:47.490 --> 00:03:48.650
这一带的土地...
All the land...

00:03:49.200 --> 00:03:50.360
都是本王子的
all this is mine.

00:03:50.540 --> 00:03:51.700
这里是本王子的封邑
Here starts the prince's principate.

00:03:52.290 --> 00:03:55.790
我要叫它Addis Ababa
I'll call this place Addis Ababa.

00:03:56.250 --> 00:03:59.370
我打算用骆驼取代牛
I’ll change it all. Out go the cows, in come the camels.

00:03:59.590 --> 00:04:01.580
骆驼
Camels?

00:04:01.670 --> 00:04:03.750
甚至引进几头河马
Even a few hippopotamus.

00:04:03.890 --> 00:04:06.260
我要走了  跟公主有约
I must go. I'm meeting with the princess.

00:04:06.720 --> 00:04:08.180
-什么时候  -现在
- When? - Now!

00:04:13.150 --> 00:04:15.190
早安  公主
Good morning, Princess!

00:04:15.730 --> 00:04:18.820
吓死我了  差点没摔死  有没有压伤你
How frightening. I almost killed myself. Did I hurt you?

00:04:18.900 --> 00:04:20.530
没啥大事
I've never been better.

00:04:20.950 --> 00:04:22.440
你一向都飞身下楼
Do you always leave the house like this?

00:04:22.620 --> 00:04:25.700
我想烧黄蜂巢  却被蜇了
I wanted to burn that wasps' nest, but I got stung.

00:04:25.750 --> 00:04:27.990
被蜇了  我给你吸吸
A wasp stung you? There? Allow me.

00:04:28.120 --> 00:04:29.540
不要动  公主
Hold still, Princess.

00:04:30.590 --> 00:04:33.370
黄蜂毒得狠
A wasp's poison is very dangerous.

00:04:33.460 --> 00:04:34.870
一定要把毒液啜出来才行
You have to get it out.

00:04:35.050 --> 00:04:38.380
-躺下  过会儿就没事了  -谢谢
- Lie down. It’ll take a while. - No, thank you.

00:04:41.140 --> 00:04:43.260
-还有哪被蜇了  -没了
- Did you get stung anywhere else? - No, thank you.

00:04:43.810 --> 00:04:46.270
好美的景色啊
What a place here! It's beautiful!

00:04:46.650 --> 00:04:49.520
鸽子畅游天际  女人从天而降  我一定要搬来
Pigeons fly, women fall from the sky. I'm moving here!

00:04:49.900 --> 00:04:53.440
他是这里的王子  他会在这里养满骆驼
It's all his! He wants to fill it with camels! He's a prince!

00:04:54.240 --> 00:04:55.270
没错
Exactly.

00:04:55.740 --> 00:04:58.360
公主  Guido王子有礼了
Prince Guido at your service, Princess.

00:04:59.580 --> 00:05:00.990
我来了
I'm coming!

00:05:01.120 --> 00:05:02.620
再见了
Goodbye, then.

00:05:03.210 --> 00:05:04.950
我该怎样谢你
How can I thank you?

00:05:05.250 --> 00:05:06.370
不用多谢
There's no need.

00:05:06.630 --> 00:05:08.750
真想谢的话...
If you really want to thank me...

00:05:09.260 --> 00:05:12.420
赏几只蛋来  给我的武士吃
I’ll take some eggs to make a nice omelet for my squire.

00:05:12.640 --> 00:05:14.550
随便拿  不要客气
Take whatever you want. It’s all yours.

00:05:14.600 --> 00:05:15.680
谢谢
Thank you!

00:05:15.970 --> 00:05:19.760
我拿两...六个吧  我来煎个蛋饼
I’ll take two... six. All right? I’ll make a nice omelet.

00:05:19.980 --> 00:05:24.060
拜拜  Eleonora  致以诚挚的问候  公主
Goodbye, Eleonora! My regards, Princess.

00:05:24.990 --> 00:05:26.180
后会有期
Farewell.

00:05:27.200 --> 00:05:31.110
Nuvolari  今晚我们有蛋饼吃
Here I am, Nuvolari! Tonight's special: omelet!

00:05:31.790 --> 00:05:33.830
这一带好多骆驼
All camels here!

00:05:42.090 --> 00:05:46.720
-哪间屋呢  -转左  快到了
- Where is this house? - Turn left. We're almost there.

00:05:46.850 --> 00:05:48.550
你叔叔也跟我们一起住
Is your uncle sleeping with us?

00:05:48.810 --> 00:05:52.060
他是酒店的头儿  在酒店都住了30年了
He's lived in the hotel for 30 years. He's the headman.

00:05:52.140 --> 00:05:55.230
那间屋子本是他的储藏室  借给我们用的
He's lending us the house. He uses it for storage.

00:05:55.360 --> 00:05:56.770
我们到了
There. We're here.

00:05:57.280 --> 00:06:00.230
那是我叔叔的马  叫罗宾汉
That's Robin Hood, my uncle's horse.

00:06:00.450 --> 00:06:03.730
这是他的马车还有他的房子
Here's my uncle's buggy and my uncle's house.

00:06:04.830 --> 00:06:06.320
屋里的那位就是我叔叔了
And inside is my uncle.

00:06:07.040 --> 00:06:09.490
叔叔  我们来了  快点  已经很晚了
Hello, dear uncle! Here we are! Hurry, it's late.

00:06:09.830 --> 00:06:10.860
汽车途中抛锚了
Here we are. The car broke down!

00:06:15.550 --> 00:06:20.340
叔叔
Uncle!

00:06:23.020 --> 00:06:25.060
-野蛮人  -他们是谁
- Barbarians. - Who were they?

00:06:25.390 --> 00:06:27.560
-只是野蛮人而已  -为何不呼救
- Barbarians. - Why didn't you cry for help?

00:06:27.560 --> 00:06:30.520
此时无声胜有声
Silence is the most powerful cry.

00:06:30.650 --> 00:06:32.020
你的诗人朋友
Is he your poet friend?

00:06:32.240 --> 00:06:35.320
我叫Ferruccio  是搞装修的
My name is Ferruccio. I'm also an upholsterer.

00:06:35.530 --> 00:06:38.780
就是这儿  一件旧货仓  地方狭窄  里面堆满了杂物
Here you are. It's an old storehouse full of odds and ends.

00:06:39.080 --> 00:06:43.030
我喜欢收藏杂物
An old passion; an odd and end in itself!

00:06:43.790 --> 00:06:45.700
收藏来有什么用
What's all this stuff for?

00:06:45.880 --> 00:06:49.630
你们要住多久都可以  我可没空陪你们
You can stay as long as you want. It's not easy to be a waiter.

00:06:50.420 --> 00:06:53.000
那张床  据说一位革命家睡过
That's the bed. Legend has it Garibaldi slept there.

00:06:53.470 --> 00:06:55.880
没什么比非必需品更必需
Nothing is more necessary than the unnecessary.

00:06:56.010 --> 00:06:56.880
野蛮人
Barbarians.

00:06:57.060 --> 00:07:00.810
市政局在Sestani街  大堂右边
The town hall is on Via Sestani, to the right after the colonnade.

00:07:00.940 --> 00:07:05.900
这是浴室  设备略有新意
The bathroom, equipped with the invention of Mr. Bidet.

00:07:06.190 --> 00:07:09.190
这里有几本书  诗人传记之类的
There are a few books here, among which The Life of Petrarch.

00:07:09.360 --> 00:07:13.490
厨房在这里  脚踏车  也就是单车
The kitchen is in there. This is a velocipede, commonly called a bike.

00:07:13.830 --> 00:07:18.450
我要回酒店了  钥匙只有一把  别弄丢了
I have to get back to the hotel. There's only one key. Don't lose it.

00:07:18.790 --> 00:07:20.790
欢迎你们的到来  罗宾汉  等等我
It's so good to see you. I'm coming, Robin Hood!

00:07:21.630 --> 00:07:23.340
我们走  罗宾汉

00:07:26.720 --> 00:07:27.800
你的叔叔很特别
What an uncle!

00:07:30.310 --> 00:07:31.550
这个城市多美丽
Look at this!

00:07:32.100 --> 00:07:35.350
我没介绍错吧  到了这儿  想做什么就做什么
Didn't I tell you? We're in a city. You can do whatever you want.

00:07:35.480 --> 00:07:38.560
没错  无拘无束  想做就做
If you want to do something, you do it.

00:07:38.650 --> 00:07:42.730
想放松吗  想大喊吗  喊吧
You want to let yourself go? You want to yell? Yell!

00:07:45.780 --> 00:07:47.940
别喊了  发什么神经
Stop it! What are you, crazy?

00:07:47.990 --> 00:07:50.950
这是市里  不是乡下
You can't act like you do in the country.

00:07:51.290 --> 00:07:54.660
怎么可以大呼小叫
You've been yelling like a madman. You can't yell!

00:07:54.800 --> 00:07:57.000
玛莉  钥匙
Mary! The key!

00:07:58.470 --> 00:08:01.500
知道了吧  不可以吵嚷
See? You can't yell.

00:08:03.140 --> 00:08:06.510
你不应该整天吟诗
Understand? If you stopped thinking so much about poetry...

00:08:06.810 --> 00:08:10.640
应该去赚赚钱  令你爸爸放心
you'd make your father happier and you'd make more money than him.

00:08:10.770 --> 00:08:12.650
对  Oreste  我正那样劝他
That's right, Oreste. That's what I tell him too.

00:08:12.820 --> 00:08:14.890
你应该踏实一点
You have to settle down!

00:08:15.070 --> 00:08:17.310
好漂亮的帽子  好看吗
What a nice hat. How does it look?

00:08:18.030 --> 00:08:20.570
-真棒  好看吗  -好看是好看  不过这帽子是我的
- Nice. How does it look? - Nice, but it's mine.

00:08:20.870 --> 00:08:22.580
我几时开工
When do I start working?

00:08:22.790 --> 00:08:24.990
你已经迟到了  赶紧开始吧
You're already late. Right away!

00:08:25.370 --> 00:08:27.660
将那椅子搬入工作间
Get that armchair and take it to the workshop.

00:08:28.130 --> 00:08:31.960
-那张吗  -对  小心
- That one? - That one. And be careful!

00:08:32.880 --> 00:08:35.460
我要去市政局  再见
Good. I'm going to the town hall. Goodbye.

00:08:35.680 --> 00:08:38.090
再见  记得规规矩矩
Goodbye, and behave yourselves...

00:08:38.390 --> 00:08:40.380
现在时势险恶
because these are hard times.

00:08:40.980 --> 00:08:42.850
可不是么
Hard, hard times!

00:08:43.020 --> 00:08:44.400
时势险恶
They're hard times?

00:08:44.980 --> 00:08:47.560
为啥呀  你有什么高见
Why, what are your political views?

00:08:48.280 --> 00:08:50.350
Benito  Adolph  老实点
Benito! Adolph! Be good!

00:08:51.660 --> 00:08:53.280
你说啥了
What did you say?

00:08:54.490 --> 00:08:57.490
我说  你有什么看法
I said, how are things going?

00:08:57.750 --> 00:08:58.910
那么再见了
Goodbye, then.

00:08:59.460 --> 00:09:03.290
小心  别撞断椅腿
Careful! You'll break the legs!

00:09:03.590 --> 00:09:04.620
再见
Goodbye!

00:09:10.470 --> 00:09:13.640
他偷了我的帽子  我不会放过他的
He pulled it off. He took my hat. I'll find him though.

00:09:15.310 --> 00:09:17.100
Benito  信不信我赏你一耳光
Benito, you're going to get a slap!

00:09:19.270 --> 00:09:22.940
申请书店营业的手续很繁复
I need to do the whole bureaucratic procedure to open a bookstore.

00:09:23.070 --> 00:09:25.150
-时间很长吗  -得好几年
- Does it take a long time? - Years.

00:09:25.780 --> 00:09:28.070
那就现在填写申请表吧
Then we'd better open a file now.

00:09:28.330 --> 00:09:31.410
先填妥申请表  交给政务官签名
First you apply, and the department head has to sign it.

00:09:32.120 --> 00:09:33.290
同时...

00:09:34.250 --> 00:09:37.950
差点压碎了鸡蛋  昨天才得到的呢
I almost scrambled my eggs. I've had them since yesterday.

00:09:38.130 --> 00:09:41.250
我都忘了  幸好没有破裂  你写下来
I forgot about them. Thank God they didn't break. Take note.

00:09:41.590 --> 00:09:43.090
本人Guido Orefice兹申请...
I, the undersigned, Guido Orefice...

00:09:43.350 --> 00:09:45.880
政务官现在没空签名
- am applying to open… - He can't sign it now!

00:09:47.890 --> 00:09:49.140
什么事
What's going on?

00:09:49.390 --> 00:09:52.270
我想请你签个名  我要开书店
I need your signature to open a bookstore.

00:09:52.860 --> 00:09:55.430
-小姐，发生了什么事  - Rodolfo先生  我告诉过他
- Miss, what's going on? - Mr. Rodolfo, I told him.

00:09:55.530 --> 00:09:57.980
-只签一个名  -不签
- Just one signature. - No, I can't.

00:09:58.110 --> 00:10:00.520
会有人接替我一小时  问他吧
My substitute will be here in an hour. Ask him.

00:10:00.660 --> 00:10:03.700
-就签一下吧  -我们一点休息
- All I need is a signature. - We close at one here!

00:10:04.830 --> 00:10:06.410
现在还有10分钟
It's ten to one.

00:10:06.670 --> 00:10:08.160
你不服气  尽管投诉
File a complaint.

00:10:09.380 --> 00:10:11.790
真黑心  他只要签个名  填份资料
Boy, is he nasty. To sign a paper, open a file,

00:10:12.420 --> 00:10:16.010
我就可以立即递申请表
all he had to do was...

00:10:16.470 --> 00:10:19.090
却硬要我等一个钟头
Now I have to wait one hour for his substitute.

00:10:19.260 --> 00:10:22.100
我要投诉  写下来  本人Guido...
I'm filing a complaint. Write, "I, the undersigned..."

00:10:25.400 --> 00:10:26.810
糟糕
What a wallop!

00:10:30.950 --> 00:10:33.230
有没有伤到  我帮你
Are you hurt? I’ll help you.

00:10:33.450 --> 00:10:35.440
我不是故意的
Come here. I didn't do it on purpose.

00:10:35.780 --> 00:10:36.860
别碰我
Don't touch me!

00:10:37.450 --> 00:10:40.990
你以后休想开书店
You can forget about your bookshop!

00:10:42.170 --> 00:10:43.030
不要戴  有蛋
No, the eggs!

00:10:46.260 --> 00:10:48.500
臭小子  我要杀了你
You scoundrel! I’ll kill you!

00:10:57.810 --> 00:10:59.890
让开
Out of the way!

00:11:06.200 --> 00:11:08.320
早安  公主
Good morning, Princess.

00:11:10.080 --> 00:11:13.030
我们能够站着见面就好
I wonder if we'll ever bump into each other standing up.

00:11:13.660 --> 00:11:15.910
对不起  我赶时间
Excuse me, but I've got to run.

00:11:16.210 --> 00:11:18.040
再见  公主
Farewell, Princess!

00:11:32.230 --> 00:11:34.310
-鸡肉  -没问题
- Chicken. - That's easy.

00:11:34.980 --> 00:11:37.770
上整只的  鸡屁股向下
It's served whole, bottom down on the plate.

00:11:38.030 --> 00:11:39.270
-可以替我切吗  -当然
"Will you cut it for me?" "Naturally."

00:11:39.490 --> 00:11:42.110
我抓稳  一刀向鸡膀下捅进去
I stick the blade under the wing

00:11:42.410 --> 00:11:43.950
将鸡腿扯掉
then I rip off the drumstick.

00:11:44.330 --> 00:11:46.120
然后起鸡胸肉
I cut the meat along the bottom of the breastbone.

00:11:46.540 --> 00:11:48.120
-扯掉鸡翅  切掉鸡胸 扒掉鸡皮
- Off go the wings, breast and skin.

00:11:48.330 --> 00:11:49.450
龙虾
Lobster

00:11:49.630 --> 00:11:51.040
易如反掌
Piece of cake, Uncle.

00:11:51.340 --> 00:11:53.540
一刀向虾翼下捅进去...
I stick the wing under the leg.

00:11:53.800 --> 00:11:57.250
起虾腿  扭龙虾  一刀...
Off goes the leg. I rip off the lobster, stick the...

00:11:57.680 --> 00:12:01.130
龙虾是甲壳类动物
Lobster is a crustacean.

00:12:01.680 --> 00:12:03.680
把这甲壳类动物...
Off goes the crust...

00:12:03.850 --> 00:12:05.350
起虾壳
of the crustacean.

00:12:05.600 --> 00:12:10.270
起虾须  虾须吃不得吧
Off go the crust and antennae. Who eats the antennae?

00:12:10.780 --> 00:12:13.350
去掉虾须  去掉龙虾
Off go the antennae, off goes the lobster.

00:12:13.820 --> 00:12:15.360
片甲不留
There's nothing left.

00:12:15.570 --> 00:12:18.610
没有龙虾  但有色香味美的鸡
We're out of lobster, but the chicken is delicious.

00:12:19.160 --> 00:12:21.400
我忘了怎样上龙虾
I don't remember how to do lobster.

00:12:21.500 --> 00:12:23.790
直接从厨房捧出来
You serve it as is.

00:12:23.830 --> 00:12:25.380
连碰也不用碰
There's no need to touch it!

00:12:25.880 --> 00:12:28.710
真容易  难怪我没记住
That's too easy. That's why I didn't remember.

00:12:28.970 --> 00:12:30.510
-继续啊  -老实点
- Continue. - Behavior!

00:12:30.630 --> 00:12:32.260
在桌旁站定  像这样
Stand by. Still, like this.

00:12:32.600 --> 00:12:34.170
-服务员  -在
"Waiter?" "Yes?"

00:12:34.350 --> 00:12:37.510
站定  候命  服务员
In position. Stand by behavior. Waiter!

00:12:45.030 --> 00:12:48.110
怎么专叫我  怎不叫其他人
Why only me? There must be other waiters, right?

00:12:50.120 --> 00:12:52.410
鞠躬  难到哪去
Bowing! Piece of cake.

00:12:54.000 --> 00:12:56.750
鞠得再低些
You bow down, further.

00:12:57.000 --> 00:13:00.950
像这个香槟瓶  45度
Like this, at a 45 degree angle, just like a champagne bottle.

00:13:01.090 --> 00:13:04.170
45度  甚至50度  55度
45 degrees, even 50, 55.

00:13:04.300 --> 00:13:07.420
90度  直角  180度
90 degrees. A right angle. 180.

00:13:07.510 --> 00:13:10.680
还得鞠多低  180度  像这样吗
How far do I bow down? 180 degrees? Like this?

00:13:11.020 --> 00:13:14.020
学向日葵  向日葵向太阳鞠躬
Think of a sunflower. They bow to the sun.

00:13:14.230 --> 00:13:16.600
鞠得太低的向日葵...
But if you see some that are too bowed down...

00:13:16.820 --> 00:13:20.480
已经枯死  你是侍者  不是下人
it means they're dead! You're serving. You're not a servant.

00:13:20.950 --> 00:13:23.620
服务是高精艺术
Serving is a supreme art.

00:13:23.820 --> 00:13:25.400
上帝是第一位侍者
God is the first servant.

00:13:26.120 --> 00:13:28.690
上帝为人服务  但上帝不是下人
God serves men, but he's not a servant to men.

00:13:29.580 --> 00:13:33.410
-没有钮  -傻子  不应该有钮
- There was no button here. - It doesn't go there, silly.

00:13:33.880 --> 00:13:36.450
我要把车开回家  还给爸爸  他还得用呢
I have to take the car back to Pop. He's counting on it.

00:13:36.670 --> 00:13:38.670
一个月后再开回去吧
You'll take it back in a month or so.

00:13:38.890 --> 00:13:42.390
不  我很快就会开回去的  你知道怎么回事吗
No, I've got to get it back soon. You know why?

00:13:42.850 --> 00:13:44.180
怎么回事
Why?

00:13:51.230 --> 00:13:54.730
-几点了  -你睡着了吗
- What? What time is it? - Were you sleeping?

00:13:54.860 --> 00:13:56.110
当然睡着
Of course I was.

00:13:56.740 --> 00:14:00.190
你能一边说一边睡
You fell asleep while talking to me!

00:14:00.450 --> 00:14:02.240
-你怎么做到的  -叔本华
- How did you do that? - Schopenhauer.

00:14:02.910 --> 00:14:03.860
叔本啥
Who?

00:14:04.630 --> 00:14:07.960
叔本华  他说过  意志决定一切
Schopenhauer says that with willpower, you can do anything.

00:14:08.300 --> 00:14:09.920
我想怎样  就能怎样
"I am what I want to be."

00:14:10.300 --> 00:14:13.830
我想睡着  于是说...
Right now I want to sleep, so I was saying to myself...

00:14:14.010 --> 00:14:16.050
睡着吧  睡着吧  于是我就睡着了
"I'm sleeping, sleeping," and I fell asleep.

00:14:16.640 --> 00:14:19.010
真神奇  也很简单
Amazing. And it's simple too.

00:14:19.310 --> 00:14:20.170
我也试试
I want to try too.

00:14:21.060 --> 00:14:24.480
睡着吧  睡着吧  睡着吧
I'm sleeping, sleeping, sleeping...

00:14:24.610 --> 00:14:27.860
不要动手  现在不是玩杂耍
Don't move your hands. You're not a juggler.

00:14:28.070 --> 00:14:31.110
这是思想的功夫  要认真  慢慢来
It's a matter of thought. It's serious, and it takes time.

00:14:31.240 --> 00:14:33.070
明天再说吧
We'll talk about it tomorrow.

00:14:34.290 --> 00:14:35.860
神奇啊
Amazing, though.

00:14:37.960 --> 00:14:39.040
醒过来
Wake up.

00:14:39.790 --> 00:14:44.670
醒过来
Wake up.

00:14:44.880 --> 00:14:46.340
又怎样  做什么
What is it now? What are you doing?

00:14:46.550 --> 00:14:48.710
-凑效了  -什么凑效了
- It totally works! - What works?

00:14:49.010 --> 00:14:52.130
叔本华  我刚刚说  醒过来
Schopenhauer. You know what I just said? "Wake up."

00:14:52.730 --> 00:14:55.730
你就立即醒了过来  这理论太不可思议了
Bam, you woke up. This theory is incredible.

00:14:56.110 --> 00:14:58.560
-好使吧  -你冲着我的耳朵喊
- How does it work? - You were yelling in my ear!

00:14:58.730 --> 00:15:00.230
我能不醒吗
That's why I woke up.

00:15:01.860 --> 00:15:05.030
-我该温柔点吗  -根本不该出声
- So I should say it quieter. - Don't say it at all!

00:15:05.280 --> 00:15:06.280
好深奥啊
It's deep.

00:15:08.790 --> 00:15:11.360
要运用精神力量
You have to think it.

00:15:15.550 --> 00:15:17.540
跑什么  慢点
Why are you running? Slow down!

00:15:17.670 --> 00:15:19.130
快点  已经迟了
Hurry up. It's late!

00:15:19.300 --> 00:15:20.960
玛莉  钥匙
Mary, the key!

00:15:23.760 --> 00:15:25.640
每天早晨  她都把钥匙扔下来
Every morning, she throws the key.

00:15:26.020 --> 00:15:27.100
看
Look!

00:15:27.310 --> 00:15:30.020
那女教师好标致啊
There's that teacher. Boy, is she pretty.

00:15:30.150 --> 00:15:31.230
连做梦都梦见她
I even dreamt about her.

00:15:31.440 --> 00:15:33.430
来  我给你介绍
Come with me. I’ll introduce you.

00:15:33.650 --> 00:15:36.110
-靠  不要动  -怎么了
- Holy smokes! Stay still! - What is it?

00:15:36.360 --> 00:15:37.910
不要动
Don't move!

00:15:38.780 --> 00:15:41.650
车上的人  是那鸡蛋淋头的混蛋
The one in the car. He's that jerk the eggs fell on.

00:15:42.080 --> 00:15:44.320
他见到我  会跟我拼命的
He'll kill me if he sees me. Be good.

00:15:44.500 --> 00:15:46.660
-他在干什么  -在说话
- What's he doing? - He's talking.

00:15:46.710 --> 00:15:48.870
-说啥呢  -我哪知道
- What's he saying? - How do I know?

00:15:49.130 --> 00:15:52.750
-他在干什么  -道别
- What's he doing? - He's saying goodbye.

00:15:53.180 --> 00:15:54.550
他的那部车和我的一模一样
He's got a car just like mine!

00:15:55.260 --> 00:15:56.010
他来了
There he is!

00:15:56.390 --> 00:15:58.630
不要动  他看到我我就死定了
Don't move. He'll kill me if he sees me!

00:15:59.520 --> 00:16:01.340
不要动  Ferruccio
Stay still, Ferruccio.

00:16:04.270 --> 00:16:06.680
公主早
Good morning, Princess!

00:16:08.490 --> 00:16:11.490
又是你  怎会这样巧
It's you again. How do you do this?

00:16:11.950 --> 00:16:15.070
是那个从天而降的公主
This is the princess who fell from the sky into my arms.

00:16:15.370 --> 00:16:18.120
他是那个替你吸取毒液的人吗
Is he the one who sucked the stinger out of your thigh?

00:16:18.290 --> 00:16:22.750
是  我们经常无意碰见
Yes. We keep meeting like this. You just suddenly show up.

00:16:23.210 --> 00:16:25.700
我们可以约见
We could make plans to meet.

00:16:26.220 --> 00:16:28.090
-今晚八点  -不  还是这样好
- Tonight at 8:00? - No, it's nicer this way.

00:16:28.390 --> 00:16:30.260
Dora  我们走  快迟到了
Let's go, Dora. You'll be late.

00:16:32.100 --> 00:16:34.850
希望可以再次遇见你
I hope we meet again suddenly.

00:16:35.190 --> 00:16:36.850
再见  公主
Farewell, Princess!

00:16:37.480 --> 00:16:40.230
见到了吧  她多迷人
Did you see her? She's pretty, huh?

00:16:40.530 --> 00:16:42.270
她喜欢我突然出现
She likes it when I suddenly appear.

00:16:50.450 --> 00:16:52.410
想不到啊
I don't believe it.

00:16:53.000 --> 00:16:55.570
黑暗
"Obscurity."

00:16:56.420 --> 00:16:57.880
你是个天才
You're a genius!

00:16:58.210 --> 00:17:00.460
越多越看不见
"The bigger it is, the less you see it."

00:17:00.590 --> 00:17:02.050
谜底是  黑暗
Solution: obscurity.

00:17:02.550 --> 00:17:03.500
了不起
Marvelous.

00:17:03.930 --> 00:17:05.760
-你自作的谜语  -不是
- Did you make that riddle up? - No,

00:17:05.970 --> 00:17:10.020
你五分钟就猜出来了  我却用了八天
but you solved it in five minutes. It took me eight days.

00:17:10.440 --> 00:17:11.600
黑暗
Obscurity!

00:17:12.360 --> 00:17:14.890
三文鱼  沙拉  和白酒一杯
Salmon, salad and a glass of white wine.

00:17:15.190 --> 00:17:17.320
我再出个谜
Listen to this one, Guido.

00:17:17.860 --> 00:17:20.100
不如轮到我出
If I may, it's my turn.

00:17:20.490 --> 00:17:23.030
我小时候  听父亲说过
My pop told me this when I was a wee boy.

00:17:23.370 --> 00:17:26.490
白雪公主切饼招待七个小矮人
"The dwarves and Snow White sit down for a bite.

00:17:26.540 --> 00:17:29.630
白雪公主切饼要切多
How fast can you guess what she serves her guests next?"

00:17:33.800 --> 00:17:35.590
相当复杂
It sounds refined.

00:17:36.590 --> 00:17:38.470
我现在就试一下
I want to solve it right now.

00:17:38.600 --> 00:17:39.970
吃完再猜吧  菜都凉了
Eat first or it'll get cold.

00:17:40.140 --> 00:17:41.970
我反正没胃口  时间太晚
I don't want to. It's too late.

00:17:42.060 --> 00:17:44.470
沙拉  三文鱼和白酒  都易消化
Salad, salmon, white wine. It's light.

00:17:44.650 --> 00:17:46.270
白雪公主...
The dwarves...

00:17:47.270 --> 00:17:49.180
和七个小矮人
... and Snow White.

00:17:52.950 --> 00:17:55.650
-厨房收了工  -是啊  怎么了
- Is the kitchen closed? - Everybody's gone. Why?

00:17:55.990 --> 00:17:59.240
有位视学官从罗马来  想吃东西
A gentleman from Rome is here from the ministry. He wants to eat.

00:17:59.500 --> 00:18:00.360
厨师收工了
The kitchen is closed.

00:18:00.750 --> 00:18:03.040
他或者会给好多小费
Oh, well, he would have given you a good tip.

00:18:03.290 --> 00:18:05.000
厨师开工了
The kitchen is open.

00:18:05.630 --> 00:18:07.170
请进
Come right in.

00:18:16.440 --> 00:18:18.480
医生  你什么都不吃吗
Doctor, you're not eating anything?

00:18:21.400 --> 00:18:23.140
白雪公主和七个小矮人…
"The dwarves and Snow White..."

00:18:25.110 --> 00:18:29.110
既然厨房收工了  来点凉菜就行
I know the kitchen is closed. Maybe a cold dish.

00:18:29.200 --> 00:18:31.190
敝店菜色精美  请随便点
It's all delicious. Take your pick.

00:18:31.750 --> 00:18:33.370
我要清淡一点的
Something light.

00:18:33.710 --> 00:18:36.460
我们有巨型牛排
Well, we've got meat, a nice heavy steak...

00:18:36.580 --> 00:18:39.500
有羊肉  腰子  酥炸肝
lamb, kidneys, some greasy breaded liver.

00:18:39.710 --> 00:18:41.370
-还有鱼呢  -鱼
- Otherwise, there's fish. - Fish.

00:18:42.840 --> 00:18:43.920
还有...
We have...

00:18:44.220 --> 00:18:45.460
肥美鲮鱼
a nice fatty turbot...

00:18:45.720 --> 00:18:48.340
白兰地汁烩香肠酿鳝
eel stuffed with fatty sausage and greased with Grand Marnier...

00:18:49.230 --> 00:18:51.380
精瘦的三文鱼
or some lean salmon--

00:18:51.900 --> 00:18:53.890
三文鱼  谢谢
The salmon, thank you.

00:18:54.150 --> 00:18:54.980
配菜呢
Side dish?

00:18:55.570 --> 00:18:56.650
还有配菜呢
There's a side dish too?

00:18:57.780 --> 00:19:01.030
任您选择  我们有香炸鲜菇
Of course. We have very, very fried mushrooms...

00:19:01.320 --> 00:19:04.820
牛油浓汁炆薯仔
buttered potatoes in Nancy butter with a flaky sauce--

00:19:05.120 --> 00:19:09.660
我只要点清淡的沙拉  没有就什么都不要
Is there a small, light salad? If not, nothing.

00:19:10.210 --> 00:19:14.620
清淡的沙拉  真可惜啊  香炸鲜菇…
A light salad? What a pity. The very, very fried mushrooms...

00:19:14.800 --> 00:19:17.250
滋味无穷  清淡沙拉…
were out of this world. So, a light salad...

00:19:17.300 --> 00:19:19.880
瘦三文鱼  一杯白酒
a lean salmon and a glass of white wine.

00:19:20.140 --> 00:19:21.800
非常好  请稍等
Perfect. As soon as possible.

00:19:22.020 --> 00:19:23.560
我会尽快的
I’ll do my best.

00:19:40.250 --> 00:19:43.620
白雪公主多久才切完饼
"How fast can you guess what she serves her guests next?"

00:19:43.750 --> 00:19:44.660
没错
Right.

00:19:45.840 --> 00:19:48.540
-白雪公主和矮人  -晚安  医生
- The dwarves and Snow White. - Good night, Doctor.

00:19:48.720 --> 00:19:50.340
晚安  天才
Good night, genius.

00:19:52.800 --> 00:19:56.220
他说什么了  白雪公主  喝茫了吧
What did he say? The dwarves? What is he, drunk?

00:19:56.730 --> 00:19:58.930
是个谜语  谜底是”七秒”
It's a riddle. "Seven seconds."

00:20:00.810 --> 00:20:04.230
答案是七秒  白雪公主和七个小矮人
"Seven seconds" is the solution. "The dwarves and Snow White."

00:20:04.360 --> 00:20:06.400
如果有七个小矮人吃饼
If there are seven dwarves dining...

00:20:06.570 --> 00:20:09.240
每人一份的话  总共就是”七秒”
and she serves seconds, that means "seven seconds."

00:20:06.570 --> 00:20:09.240
second有”份”和”秒”两个意思

00:20:09.660 --> 00:20:13.700
Lessing医生太忠直老实了
Doctor Lessing is a physician, a very serious person.

00:20:14.000 --> 00:20:17.250
但他猜谜猜上瘾了  废寝忘食的
But he's obsessed with riddles. He loses sleep over them.

00:20:20.170 --> 00:20:23.210
请问方济各学校...
Excuse me. The "Francesco Petrarca" school.

00:20:24.260 --> 00:20:27.960
那间小学  我认识那里的一位老师
The elementary school? A friend of mine teaches there. It's beautiful.

00:20:28.180 --> 00:20:29.760
离这里不远  怎么了
It's not far from here. Why?

00:20:30.060 --> 00:20:32.810
好  我可以睡多半个钟头
Good. I can sleep an extra half hour.

00:20:33.020 --> 00:20:35.590
你明早非得去学校不可么
Do you have to go to that school tomorrow morning?

00:20:36.020 --> 00:20:38.400
八点半必须到
They're expecting me at 8:30.

00:20:44.910 --> 00:20:48.110
各位同学  请安静  我有话说
Please, children, silence! A moment of attention.

00:20:48.290 --> 00:20:50.830
视学官很快就要来了
The inspector from Rome will be here shortly.

00:20:51.330 --> 00:20:53.490
大家要给他个好印象
I want to make a good impression on him.

00:20:53.670 --> 00:20:57.420
他说的话  大家都要用心听
Listen very quietly and carefully to what he says.

00:20:57.420 --> 00:21:00.630
他将会报道美丽祖国的大事
He'll tell us some very important things about our beautiful country.

00:21:01.260 --> 00:21:04.010
校长  视学官到了
The inspector is here, ma’am.

00:21:04.310 --> 00:21:06.800
这么快啊
He's already here? He's early!

00:21:07.270 --> 00:21:08.890
坐下  Roberto
Sit down, Roberto!

00:21:13.030 --> 00:21:15.400
起立
All rise!

00:21:19.740 --> 00:21:21.530
早上好  公主
Good morning, Princess.

00:21:24.710 --> 00:21:28.240
早上好  视学官  我是这儿的校长
Good morning, Mr. Inspector. I'm the principal.

00:21:28.500 --> 00:21:30.580
这几位是敝校的教员
These are some of our teachers.

00:21:33.180 --> 00:21:34.210
好
Good.

00:21:36.970 --> 00:21:38.050
那么...
Therefore...

00:21:40.350 --> 00:21:43.940
你在本区任教多少年了
How many years have you taught in this school district?

00:21:44.070 --> 00:21:45.100
16年
Sixteen.

00:21:47.490 --> 00:21:50.440
教育部今年通过的教育方案...
Are you up to date with the ongoing...

00:21:50.490 --> 00:21:52.700
你有没有好好领会
school program approved by the ministry this year?

00:21:52.830 --> 00:21:53.990
有
Yes.

00:21:56.160 --> 00:21:59.860
有没有阅读学童保健通告
Did you read the bulletin regarding childhood hygiene?

00:22:00.460 --> 00:22:01.870
当然有
Of course.

00:22:04.550 --> 00:22:06.210
你星期天都干什么
What are you doing on Sunday?

00:22:07.680 --> 00:22:08.880
我说的星期天是指…
No, I mean, Sunday is…

00:22:09.350 --> 00:22:12.430
圣母节  你都做什么
