I'm sick and tired of these Visigoths.

00:51:25.900 --> 00:51:27.890
早安
Good morning.

00:51:27.990 --> 00:51:29.610
全部半价
Everything's half price.

00:51:29.950 --> 00:51:31.140
-Guido Orefice
- Guido Orefice?

00:51:31.740 --> 00:51:33.150
正是我
That's me.

00:51:33.490 --> 00:51:35.370
请到市政局去
You have to come to the prefect's.

00:51:35.500 --> 00:51:36.660
又要去
Again?

00:51:37.250 --> 00:51:38.960
-他去过  -走吧
- He already went. - Let's go.

00:51:39.080 --> 00:51:40.410
为什么
Why?

00:51:42.960 --> 00:51:45.290
-那人跟你一起  -是  走吧
- Is that man with you? - Yes. Let's go.

00:51:46.130 --> 00:51:47.160
行
All right.

00:51:47.510 --> 00:51:48.840
我也去
I'm coming too.

00:51:49.260 --> 00:51:51.550
不要去  我不会去太久  对吗?
No. You stay here. It won't take long, will it?

00:51:51.720 --> 00:51:53.000
很快回来
Not long at all.

00:51:54.270 --> 00:51:57.020
Joshua  好好招呼客人
Joshua, make sure you treat the customers good!

00:51:57.730 --> 00:51:59.110
我很快回来
I'll be right back.

00:53:02.140 --> 00:53:03.690
我要这本书
I'll take this one.

00:53:03.900 --> 00:53:05.470
5里拉
It costs five lire.

00:53:05.610 --> 00:53:09.310
上面写着10里拉
No, it says ten lire.

00:53:09.530 --> 00:53:11.480
全部半价
Everything's half price.

00:53:14.080 --> 00:53:17.330
交给你妈妈  告诉她...
Give this to your mom and tell her…

00:53:17.500 --> 00:53:18.780
是外婆的
it's from Grandma.

00:53:19.000 --> 00:53:22.200
我从未见过外婆
I've never seen my grandma before.

00:53:22.590 --> 00:53:23.780
想见吗
Would you like to meet her?

00:53:24.130 --> 00:53:24.990
想
Yes.

00:53:26.380 --> 00:53:28.370
你明天就见得到
You'll meet her tomorrow.

00:53:28.590 --> 00:53:29.670
-明天  -嗯
- Tomorrow? - Yes.

00:53:30.010 --> 00:53:32.550
因为明天是你生日
Because tomorrow is your birthday...

00:53:32.890 --> 00:53:35.640
你外婆会带份大礼来
and your grandma will come and bring you a nice present.

00:53:35.810 --> 00:53:37.640
新的坦克
A new tank?

00:53:38.100 --> 00:53:40.350
不  令你惊喜的礼物
No, a surprise.

00:53:41.400 --> 00:53:42.980
把这封信交给你妈妈
Give the letter to your mom.

00:53:44.110 --> 00:53:45.270
拜拜  Joshua
Bye, Joshua.

00:53:45.570 --> 00:53:48.060
外婆  你零钱落了
You forgot your change, Grandma.

00:53:54.330 --> 00:53:55.580
谢谢
Thank you.

00:53:56.460 --> 00:53:58.540
-你什么时候回来  -一个钟头左右
- When are you coming? - In an hour or so.

00:53:58.960 --> 00:54:01.540
我去找叔叔  或者他那里有剩饭
I’m going to stop by my uncle's to see if he'll bring some leftovers.

00:54:02.760 --> 00:54:05.380
-外婆怎么说  -她明天来
- Then what did Grandma say? - She's coming tomorrow.

00:54:08.390 --> 00:54:09.470
早就该来
It's about time!

00:54:09.940 --> 00:54:14.480
犹太店铺
JEWISH STORE

00:54:11.790 --> 00:54:14.580
-该你洗澡了  -我不想洗
- It's time for your bath now. - I don't want to take one.

00:54:14.980 --> 00:54:17.560
-去洗澡  -我星期五洗过
- Go take a bath. - I took one on Friday.

00:54:17.740 --> 00:54:19.360
他说得对
He's right.

00:54:19.820 --> 00:54:21.320
你去换衬衫
You change your shirt.

00:54:21.450 --> 00:54:24.200
-我星期四换过  -别忘记把花摘掉
- I changed it on Thursday! - Don't forget the flowers!

00:54:24.540 --> 00:54:26.360
还在外面  我已经摘了
They're outside. I already picked them.

00:54:26.660 --> 00:54:30.330
-我也去  爸爸  -你要洗澡  小顽固
- I'll come with you, Pop! - You have to take a bath, stubborn!

00:54:30.840 --> 00:54:32.160
就不洗
I don't want to take one!

00:54:33.760 --> 00:54:35.500
快点  我要去接外婆
Hurry up. I have to go pick Grandma up.

00:54:43.390 --> 00:54:46.230
-想把鲜花放在哪   -放下  我等会插
- Where do you want the flowers? - Set them down. I'll be right there.

00:54:56.280 --> 00:54:58.240
我星期五洗过
l took one on Friday!

00:55:04.000 --> 00:55:05.830
Joshua呢
Do you know where Joshua is?

00:55:06.090 --> 00:55:07.910
一定在房里
He must be in there.

00:55:08.170 --> 00:55:09.960
收拾一下好吗
Will you put those things in order?

00:55:10.050 --> 00:55:12.340
花很漂亮  拿来给我看看好吗
Why don't you show me the flowers? They look so beautiful.

00:55:12.550 --> 00:55:15.050
是很漂亮  你要看吗  我给他们拿过来
They are. I'll bring them right over. You want to see the flowers?

00:55:15.350 --> 00:55:19.050
这就拿过来
I'll make them come right over.

00:55:19.440 --> 00:55:21.100
来吧  花朵
Come, flowers!

00:55:21.270 --> 00:55:22.520
来吧  小柜
Come, nightstand!

00:55:22.690 --> 00:55:24.150
Schopenhauer  意志力  小柜来
Schopenhauer, willpower, I want the nightstand to come here.

00:55:24.900 --> 00:55:26.400
小柜来
Nightstand, come.

00:55:28.120 --> 00:55:30.160
小柜停
Stop, nightstand!

00:55:30.660 --> 00:55:33.410
小柜不洗澡  好脏
The nightstand seems very dirty to me.

00:55:34.410 --> 00:55:36.540
早安  公主
Good morning, Princess!

00:55:41.630 --> 00:55:43.620
他已经识字了吗
He can already read and write?

00:55:43.800 --> 00:55:46.590
-识了一年了  -你教得真好
- For over a year now. - You did a good job.

00:55:46.800 --> 00:55:48.460
我们到了
We're here.

00:55:48.770 --> 00:55:50.390
我扶你下车
I'll help you get out.

00:55:50.730 --> 00:55:52.430
我自己可以
No, l can do it myself.

00:56:10.000 --> 00:56:11.830
Dora  什么事
Dora, what's wrong?

00:56:32.610 --> 00:56:34.240
我们到了没有
Are we there?

00:56:34.950 --> 00:56:36.490
没有  到了十字路口
No, it's a crossing.

00:56:36.820 --> 00:56:39.360
我们究竟要到哪去
Will you tell me where we're going now?

00:56:39.950 --> 00:56:41.530
到哪去  什么意思
What do you mean, where?

00:56:42.290 --> 00:56:44.610
你都问过好多次了  我们要去...
You asked me a thousand times. We're going...

00:56:45.380 --> 00:56:47.780
一个地方  那地方叫什么来着
to the place... What's it called?

00:56:48.510 --> 00:56:49.500
我们要到...
We're going...

00:56:49.800 --> 00:56:50.660
要到哪里去
Where are we going?

00:56:51.090 --> 00:56:54.960
今天是什么日子  你的生日啊
What day is it today? Today is your birthday!

00:56:55.600 --> 00:56:58.850
你一直说  你想旅行
You've always said you wanted to go on a trip!

00:56:59.060 --> 00:57:02.150
为了这趟旅行  我筹备了好几个月
It took me months to plan this whole thing.

00:57:02.440 --> 00:57:05.110
知道我们到哪里去吗
You know where we're going?

00:57:06.240 --> 00:57:08.230
我答应了妈妈  不能说
I can't tell you. I promised Mom I wouldn't tell.

00:57:08.490 --> 00:57:10.280
说出来  她会生气的
You know how she is. She'll get mad.

00:57:10.410 --> 00:57:12.360
总之保证你会满意
It makes me laugh.

00:57:12.450 --> 00:57:15.370
我小时候  爸爸也计划了一次旅行
My pop planned something like this for me when l was little too.

00:57:15.580 --> 00:57:18.830
真的好…  好好玩
It was so... Boy, it was funny!

00:57:21.630 --> 00:57:23.950
先不告诉你
I'm not going to tell you.

00:57:27.220 --> 00:57:29.260
等你自己看看
I want you to see for yourself.

00:57:29.560 --> 00:57:31.300
给你来个惊喜
It's a surprise. You know, it's really...

00:57:31.640 --> 00:57:34.510
保证你满意
It really makes me laugh.

00:57:34.770 --> 00:57:36.560
我累了
I'm tired.

00:57:37.730 --> 00:57:40.980
睡觉吧
Go to sleep.

00:57:46.950 --> 00:57:48.950
他们带我们到哪处去
Where are we going? Where are they taking us?

00:58:09.440 --> 00:58:12.890
现在几点了  我们准时出发
What time is it? We're leaving right on time.

00:58:13.610 --> 00:58:15.190
多么有效率啊
What organization!

00:58:15.360 --> 00:58:17.850
-你没坐过火车  -没有  很棒吗
- You've never taken a train, huh? - No. Is it nice?

00:58:18.120 --> 00:58:19.150
很棒
It's really nice!

00:58:19.620 --> 00:58:21.580
里面全部是木造的  人人都站着
It's all wooden inside. Everybody stands up.

00:58:21.740 --> 00:58:22.950
没有座位
There's not one seat.

00:58:23.080 --> 00:58:26.200
-一个座位都没有吗  -火车怎会有座位
- There aren't any seats? - What? Seats on a train?

00:58:26.460 --> 00:58:28.620
你真土  没坐过火车吧
It's obvious you've never been on one!

00:58:28.750 --> 00:58:31.760
人人都要站着  挤得很近
No, everybody stands real close together.

00:58:32.470 --> 00:58:35.840
见到这条长龙了吗  我刚刚抢到了票
Do you see this line? I got the last tickets just in time!

00:58:36.680 --> 00:58:39.090
Eliseo叔叔  快点  否则赶不上了
Hurry up, Uncle Eliseo.

00:58:39.430 --> 00:58:41.470
我不想听到他们说  太晚了  回家吧
I don't want them to say, "Too late. It's full. Go back home."

00:58:41.770 --> 00:58:44.310
我们定了位  借下光
Wait up. We've got a reservation! Leave some room for us!

00:58:45.020 --> 00:58:47.400
看  人龙多长
Look at this line!

00:58:48.650 --> 00:58:51.110
到了  我们定了位
Here we are! We made a reservation!

00:58:54.080 --> 00:58:55.700
谢谢
Thank you!

00:58:59.000 --> 00:59:00.410
需要帮助吗
May l help you?

00:59:01.380 --> 00:59:04.000
必定有误会
There's been a mistake.

00:59:04.300 --> 00:59:06.120
什么误会
What mistake?

00:59:06.590 --> 00:59:08.630
我丈夫和儿子在那车上
My husband and son are on that train.

00:59:10.430 --> 00:59:12.420
你丈夫叫什么
What's your husband's name?

00:59:12.770 --> 00:59:14.430
Guido Orefice
Guido Orefice.

00:59:20.690 --> 00:59:22.520
Orefice的儿子
Joshua Orefice...

00:59:22.610 --> 00:59:24.600
Orefice的叔叔
and Eliseo Orefice

00:59:24.780 --> 00:59:26.060
都在那节车上
are on that train too.

00:59:26.910 --> 00:59:28.650
没有误会
There's no mistake.

00:59:30.450 --> 00:59:32.330
我也要上那节车
I want to get on that train too.

00:59:34.460 --> 00:59:36.420
准备好了
We're all ready.

00:59:36.630 --> 00:59:38.170
起程吧
Send them off then.

00:59:38.420 --> 00:59:39.620
起程
Go, leave!

00:59:42.300 --> 00:59:44.300
回去吧  太太
Go back home, ma’am.

00:59:45.520 --> 00:59:47.090
我想上车
I want to get on that train.

00:59:56.030 --> 00:59:58.350
让我上车
Let me get on that train!

01:00:29.570 --> 01:00:30.430
妈妈来了
Mom's here!

01:00:33.780 --> 01:00:35.860
他们停下火车  让妈妈上来
They stopped the train to let Mom get on.

01:02:40.440 --> 01:02:41.850
Eliseo叔叔
Uncle Eliseo.

01:03:21.660 --> 01:03:24.910
看清楚没有  好玩吗  累吗
Are you happy? Did you see this place? Are you tired?

01:03:25.830 --> 01:03:28.990
-我不喜欢火车  -我也不喜欢
- I didn't like the train. – Me, either.

01:03:29.460 --> 01:03:31.170
我们会坐巴士回家
We'll take the bus back.

01:03:31.330 --> 01:03:34.750
我们要坐巴士走  有座位的巴士
We're taking the bus back! The one with the seats in it!

01:03:34.960 --> 01:03:36.790
-我对他们说了  -说得好
- I told them. - It's better.

01:03:36.970 --> 01:03:39.500
看到了吗  井井有条
You see? It's all organized!

01:03:39.970 --> 01:03:43.390
看到人龙了吗  大家得排队进去
Did you see that line? People are lined up to get inside!

01:03:43.850 --> 01:03:47.100
人人都想进去
Everybody wants to get in!

01:03:47.520 --> 01:03:49.600
他们在玩什么游戏
What game is this?

01:03:50.110 --> 01:03:50.970
对了
That's it!

01:03:51.480 --> 01:03:52.940
这是个游戏
It's that game where...

01:03:53.490 --> 01:03:55.640
我们一起玩…
It's the game...

01:03:55.910 --> 01:04:00.150
的游戏
We're all players.

01:04:01.750 --> 01:04:04.320
玩游戏必须守规矩
It's all organized. The game is...

01:04:04.540 --> 01:04:07.380
男人一边  女人一边
the men are over here, the women are over there.

01:04:07.550 --> 01:04:10.330
还有军人  他们主持游戏
Then there's the soldiers. They give us our schedule.

01:04:10.670 --> 01:04:12.750
很严厉  没那么简单的
It's hard, you know. It's not easy.

01:04:13.470 --> 01:04:17.000
谁一犯错  谁就要回家去
lf somebody makes a mistake, they get sent right home.

01:04:17.310 --> 01:04:19.020
就是说  你要很小心
That means you have to be very careful.

01:04:19.480 --> 01:04:22.890
但你赢  你就得到奖品
But if you win, you get first prize!

01:04:23.020 --> 01:04:25.230
什么奖
What's the prize?

01:04:25.230 --> 01:04:27.140
头奖
First prize!

01:04:28.950 --> 01:04:31.570
-坦克  -我已经有一辆了
- It's a tank. - I already have one.

01:04:31.870 --> 01:04:34.360
这是辆真正的坦克
This one's a real tank!

01:04:34.500 --> 01:04:35.690
闪闪新
Brand new!

01:04:35.830 --> 01:04:37.620
真的坦克
Real?

01:04:38.130 --> 01:04:40.700
真的  我本来不想告诉你
Yes! I didn't want to tell you.

01:04:48.180 --> 01:04:49.920
叔叔去哪里了
Where's Uncle Eliseo going?

01:04:50.310 --> 01:04:52.840
他属于另一组  大家分成组
He's on another team. It's all organized.

01:04:53.100 --> 01:04:55.010
再见  叔叔
Bye, Uncle!

01:04:57.820 --> 01:04:59.970
真正的坦克
A real tank.

01:05:14.420 --> 01:05:16.290
看  没有骗你吧
What did l tell you?

01:05:17.340 --> 01:05:18.620
顶瓜瓜
Fabulous!

01:05:19.050 --> 01:05:20.130
环境一流
What a place!

01:05:20.430 --> 01:05:23.630
快点  别让人霸占我们的地方
Hurry up or they'll steal our places.

01:05:24.060 --> 01:05:25.170
我们订了床位  两张单人床
We've got a reservation. Two singles!

01:05:25.770 --> 01:05:28.220
借一借
Coming through!

01:05:28.690 --> 01:05:30.510
那是我们的
There's our place!

01:05:35.950 --> 01:05:37.900
我们睡在一起
This is our bed. We'll sleep real close.

01:05:40.200 --> 01:05:43.950
这里又脏又臭  我要到妈妈那里
It's ugly here. It smells. I want to be with Mommy.

01:05:44.620 --> 01:05:46.120
我们会的
We will be!

01:05:46.250 --> 01:05:47.200
我肚子饿
I'm hungry!

01:05:47.420 --> 01:05:48.500
我们会有东西吃的
We'll eat!

01:05:49.130 --> 01:05:51.800
他们都很凶  呼呼喝喝的
Plus they're really mean here! They yell!

01:05:52.340 --> 01:05:56.390
他们不得不凶  人人都在争头奖
They yell because everybody wants first prize. They have to be tough.

01:05:56.970 --> 01:05:59.260
我什么时候才能看到妈妈
Can l see Mommy?

01:05:59.850 --> 01:06:01.310
游戏玩完就能了
When the game's over.

01:06:01.520 --> 01:06:02.800
游戏什么时候玩完
When's it over?

01:06:04.770 --> 01:06:07.530
你要得到一千分
You have to get a thousand points.

01:06:08.700 --> 01:06:10.980
谁得到一千分  谁就有坦克
Whoever gets a thousand points wins a tank.

01:06:11.320 --> 01:06:14.080
我不相信  我们有点心吃吗
I don't believe you. Are we getting a snack?

01:06:14.370 --> 01:06:16.240
点心
A snack?

01:06:17.290 --> 01:06:19.330
我去问问  这里都是熟人
Just ask. We're all friends here.

01:06:19.540 --> 01:06:22.290
-看看谁来了  他叫什么  - Bartolomeo
- Look who's here. What's his name? - Bartolomeo.

01:06:22.800 --> 01:06:24.500
问你点事儿
Let me ask you something.

01:06:24.760 --> 01:06:28.340
那个派果酱面包的人来了没有
Did the guy who hands out the bread and jam already come by?

01:06:29.470 --> 01:06:32.590
真倒霉  我们刚刚错过了
Darn it all! We missed him by a second!

01:06:33.140 --> 01:06:36.260
但他会再来  对不对
He'll come back again though, won't he?

01:06:36.770 --> 01:06:38.230
他会再来
He's coming back.

01:06:45.660 --> 01:06:46.740
他在说什么?
What did he say?

01:06:46.830 --> 01:06:48.730
他问谁懂德语
He asked if anyone speaks German.

01:06:48.950 --> 01:06:51.030
他要解释营中规矩
He's going to explain the camp's rules.

01:06:54.460 --> 01:06:56.540
-你懂德语吗  -不懂
- Do you speak German? - No.

01:07:06.350 --> 01:07:09.600
既来之则安之  游戏开始吧
The game starts now. Whoever's here is here, whoever's not is not.

01:07:13.020 --> 01:07:15.230
先得一千分就胜出
The first one to get a thousand points wins.

01:07:15.400 --> 01:07:16.690
奖品是辆真坦克
The prize is a tank!

01:07:18.280 --> 01:07:19.530
真是个幸运儿
Lucky him!

01:07:28.000 --> 01:07:31.120
每天播音宣布谁领先
Every day we'll announce who's in the lead from that loudspeaker.

01:07:31.460 --> 01:07:34.170
得最少分的人要在背后...
The one with the least points has to wear a sign saying "jackass"...

01:07:34.510 --> 01:07:36.250
吊上个"蠢材"招牌
right here on his back.

01:07:43.390 --> 01:07:46.350
我们士兵扮坏蛋  又呼又喝
We play the part of the real mean guys who yell.

01:07:46.570 --> 01:07:48.850
谁害怕  谁得的分就少
Whoever's scared loses points.

01:08:03.210 --> 01:08:05.880
在三个情况下  你们分数全失
You'll lose your points for three things.

01:08:05.960 --> 01:08:09.300
一  哭
One, if you cry.

01:08:09.680 --> 01:08:12.350
二  要找妈妈
Two, if you want to see your mommy.

01:08:12.510 --> 01:08:15.880
三  肚饿要吃点心
Three, if you're hungry and you want a snack.

01:08:16.230 --> 01:08:17.640
不要妄想
Forget about it!

01:08:26.570 --> 01:08:28.980
肚饿很容易丢分
It's easy to lose points for being hungry.

01:08:29.240 --> 01:08:31.200
昨天我丢了40分...
Just yesterday l lost 40 points...

01:08:31.330 --> 01:08:33.650
因为我一定要吃果酱面包
because l absolutely had to have a jam sandwich.

01:08:35.750 --> 01:08:36.860
杏酱面包
Apricot jam!

01:08:38.590 --> 01:08:40.250
他要草莓酱的
He wanted strawberry.

01:08:46.760 --> 01:08:49.600
棒棒糖你们不会有得吃
Don't ask for any lollipops. You won't get any.

01:08:49.770 --> 01:08:51.390
统统给我们吃
We eat them all!

01:08:53.310 --> 01:08:55.140
我昨天就吃掉20个
I ate 20 of them yesterday!

01:08:56.320 --> 01:08:58.110
吃到我肚子痛
What a stomachache.

01:08:58.610 --> 01:08:59.890
但确实美味
But they sure were good.

01:09:00.820 --> 01:09:01.990
还用说吗
You bet.

01:09:10.710 --> 01:09:13.170
说得太快了真抱歉  因为在玩捉迷藏
Sorry if I'm going so fast, but I'm playing hide and seek.

01:09:13.510 --> 01:09:15.410
我要走了  否则就被抓到了
I have to go now or they'll find me.

01:09:25.350 --> 01:09:29.140
有问题  问Bartolomeo  他通天晓地
Don't ask me anything. Ask Bartolomeo. He knows everything.

01:09:29.280 --> 01:09:31.600
他说什么  别忘记告诉我
Don't forget to tell me what he said too.

01:09:32.150 --> 01:09:34.110
一千分吗
A thousand points?

01:09:34.280 --> 01:09:36.360
没骗你吧  真的好玩
I told you we're going to have fun!

01:09:36.990 --> 01:09:38.780
这些人有病
These guys are crazy!

01:09:38.950 --> 01:09:42.540
铁砧百公斤重  这里三千度热
This has to weigh a hundred kilos! It's got to be 3,000 degrees in here!

01:09:42.790 --> 01:09:45.160
Vittorino  我捱不住
Vittorino, I can't cope anymore!

01:09:45.500 --> 01:09:47.830
-搬一个就捱不住了  -还要搬啊
- After only the first one? - Why, are there more to move?

01:09:48.550 --> 01:09:50.010
还要搬  搬到今晚
We're here until tonight!

01:09:50.050 --> 01:09:54.180
Bartolomeo  他们带你去哪里?
Bartolomeo, what happened? Where are they taking you?

01:09:54.310 --> 01:09:56.350
去医院  我胳膊受伤了
To the hospital. l hurt my arm.

01:09:58.350 --> 01:10:00.180
我们死定了
We're going to die here!

01:10:00.650 --> 01:10:04.350
我捱不住了  我要把它放下
I can't take it anymore! I'm putting this down.

01:10:04.530 --> 01:10:08.390
我不做  他们会怎样
I'll tell them I can't do it. What can they do to me?

01:10:08.700 --> 01:10:09.730
会杀掉你
They'll kill you!

01:10:10.620 --> 01:10:14.150
-搬去哪里  -下面
- Where does this thing go? - Down there.

01:10:14.460 --> 01:10:17.120
惨了  我死定了
Good Lord! I'll never make it!

01:10:23.680 --> 01:10:28.420
这里肯定有一万度
It's got to be 1 0,000 degrees in here!

01:10:57.970 --> 01:10:59.380
爸爸
Pop!

01:11:14.950 --> 01:11:17.950
看  我的制服不错吧
Look here! See? It's nice, huh?

01:11:20.450 --> 01:11:22.110
我们参加了
We're signed up.

01:11:22.960 --> 01:11:25.330
我报名的时候
When I got there to sign up...

01:11:25.630 --> 01:11:27.870
公证说...
the referee was there and he said...

01:11:28.250 --> 01:11:30.050
名单上没有你两父子的名字
"No, you and your son aren't on the list.

01:11:30.340 --> 01:11:33.670
你没有交报名费
You didn't pay your dues."

01:11:34.140 --> 01:11:36.050
气得我差点晕过去
I almost fell over.

01:11:36.260 --> 01:11:39.680
他说  你们回家吧  我说  你才回去呢
He said, "You can go home." l said, "No, you go home!

01:11:40.190 --> 01:11:42.310
Joshua和我报了名
"Joshua and l signed up.

01:11:42.080 --> 01:11:44.290
拿号码来
Give me my number!"

01:11:44.460 --> 01:11:46.920
于是给了我一个号码
In fact, they gave me one. Look.

01:11:47.780 --> 01:11:51.030
我叫他们印在胳膊上  万无一失
I had them put it here, too, just in case.

01:11:51.620 --> 01:11:53.820
看  你爸爸...
See what a nice place...

01:11:53.950 --> 01:11:56.740
带了你去一个顶瓜瓜的地方
your pop takes you to?

01:11:58.670 --> 01:12:01.240
你有没有和其他孩子玩
Did you play with the other kids?

01:12:01.460 --> 01:12:04.300
有  但他们不懂规矩
Yes, but they don't know the rules.

01:12:04.470 --> 01:12:07.720
他们说头奖不是坦克
They said it isn't true that first prize is a tank.

01:12:08.010 --> 01:12:09.970
也不懂得计分
They don't know anything about the points.

01:12:10.680 --> 01:12:13.800
你不要相信他们  他们狡猾着呢
Did you fall for that? They're as sly as foxes.

01:12:13.940 --> 01:12:16.140
他们想赢你  你不要相信
They want to beat you! Are you joking?

01:12:16.310 --> 01:12:19.350
没有坦克  怎么可能
There's no tank? Don't you believe them!

01:12:19.860 --> 01:12:22.190
我们今天得到几分
How many points did we get today?

01:12:22.620 --> 01:12:24.380
50
Fifty.

01:12:24.780 --> 01:12:27.650
48  他们扣了我两分
Forty-eight. They took two points away from me because...

01:12:28.040 --> 01:12:29.740
因为我跳房子的时候...
I tripped while l was...

01:12:30.210 --> 01:12:31.400
拌倒了
playing hopscotch.

01:12:33.460 --> 01:12:37.510
我们今天玩得好开心
We laughed like crazy today! l died laughing!

01:12:37.630 --> 01:12:40.040
认真过把瘾
Boy, did l have fun!

01:12:40.590 --> 01:12:43.130
巴不得明天立即来到
I can't wait to start all over again tomorrow!

01:12:43.760 --> 01:12:46.010
可以玩跳房子  拔河
Hopscotch, tug of war…

01:12:46.060 --> 01:12:47.520
和团团转
and ring around the rosy.

01:12:47.940 --> 01:12:51.060
游戏花款样多多  多到我想不起来
Every game. I don't even remember all of them.

01:12:51.110 --> 01:12:53.600
我说  你们玩得太疯  累死我了
"You guys are obsessed! Stop! I'm tired!" I said.

01:12:53.450 --> 01:12:54.280
Listen.
听着

01:12:54.320 --> 01:12:57.020
有没有吃过东西
Did you eat something?

01:12:57.280 --> 01:12:59.400
有  但我没要点心
Yes, but l didn't ask for a snack.

01:12:59.990 --> 01:13:03.360
乖孩子  就是说你也得到了12分
Good boy! That means you got 12 points too!

01:13:03.660 --> 01:13:06.950
我48  你12
Forty-eight for me, twelve for you.

01:13:05.710 --> 01:13:07.000
一共60分
Sixty points.

01:13:07.250 --> 01:13:10.340
60分你有奖
This is what you get when you get up to 60.

01:13:10.510 --> 01:13:14.010
只是面包  没有果酱
A plain piece of bread, no jam.

01:13:14.180 --> 01:13:15.670
吃吧
Here, eat this.

01:13:19.020 --> 01:13:22.020
-60分多不多  -还用问吗
- Is 60 points a lot? - Are you kidding?

01:13:22.350 --> 01:13:24.010
当然多
It sure is!

01:13:27.780 --> 01:13:30.350
看谁来了  Bartolomeo
Look who's here! Bartolomeo!

01:13:30.700 --> 01:13:32.570
情况怎样
How'd it go?

01:13:32.820 --> 01:13:34.860
差点没命  我领了20
Any worse than this; l got 20 of them.

01:13:39.500 --> 01:13:42.250
我们比他分高
We got more than him.

01:13:42.250 --> 01:13:45.460
我们领先呢  别告诉他
Don't tell him that. We're in the lead!

01:13:54.310 --> 01:13:56.980
我说过  小孩  老妪不准出来
I already told you: no children or old ladies!

01:13:57.270 --> 01:13:59.390
回去  你不是劳动分子
Back inside! You don't work!

01:13:59.610 --> 01:14:01.680
其他人  下楼去
The rest, downstairs!

01:14:03.240 --> 01:14:05.990
快走吧  孩子们  这边去
Let's go, girls, quickly. Come on. This way!

01:14:07.370 --> 01:14:09.820
这女兵一来就发狠
That one's new. She learned right away.

01:14:10.200 --> 01:14:13.450
门口那女兵  初来时相当好相处
The lady at the door, she seemed nice when she first came.

01:14:13.750 --> 01:14:15.370
现在变得最凶
She's the worst of all!

01:14:15.590 --> 01:14:17.830
起码她不派老妇和小孩去劳动
At least she didn't send the old ladies and children to work.

01:14:18.590 --> 01:14:21.880
老妇和小孩不用劳动  但要死
They don't send old people and kids to work because they kill them!

01:14:22.140 --> 01:14:24.840
他们被派去洗澡
One of these days they'll call them to take a shower.

01:14:25.100 --> 01:14:26.760
小朋友  洗澡啦
"Children, shower time!"

01:14:26.970 --> 01:14:30.180
其实  去的是毒气室
The truth is, they make them shower there in the gas chamber.

01:14:37.450 --> 01:14:38.730
下楼
Downstairs!

01:14:43.580 --> 01:14:45.450
我怎捱得下去?
How can l do this?

01:14:45.710 --> 01:14:47.450
Vittorino
Vittorino!

01:14:48.750 --> 01:14:51.840
这些铁砧从哪里来
Where'd they find all these anvils?

01:14:52.010 --> 01:14:53.250
爸爸
Pop!

01:14:55.720 --> 01:14:58.010
你来干什么  你不应该来
Why are you here? You're not supposed to be here!

01:14:58.640 --> 01:14:59.800
走开
Go away!

01:15:00.140 --> 01:15:01.720
为什么不跟其他孩子一起呢
Why aren't you with the other kids?

01:15:02.520 --> 01:15:03.550
他们说...
They said...

01:15:03.690 --> 01:15:07.730
小孩今天都要洗澡  我不想洗
all us kids have to take a shower today, and l don't want to.

01:15:08.570 --> 01:15:10.110
洗澡去吧
Go take a shower!

01:15:10.320 --> 01:15:11.180
不去
No!

01:15:12.320 --> 01:15:13.860
我就不去
I'm not going to.

01:15:14.280 --> 01:15:15.530
给我洗澡去
Go take a shower!

01:15:16.790 --> 01:15:18.610
你在这里干什么
What are you doing here?

01:15:20.370 --> 01:15:22.250
我们在制造...
We're making...

01:15:22.790 --> 01:15:25.000
坦克
a tank.

01:15:25.510 --> 01:15:28.540
我们正在制造  还没有造完坦克的轮带
We're building the tank. We're still working on the tracks.

01:15:28.630 --> 01:15:30.670
我们做得太慢
We're running slow.

01:15:32.470 --> 01:15:35.090
你不可以留在这里  去洗澡
You can't stay here. Go take your shower!

01:15:35.640 --> 01:15:37.970
我不想洗
I don't want to!

01:15:38.770 --> 01:15:42.190
小顽固  我会告诉你妈  扣你10分
You stubborn thing! I'll tell Mom! Ten points off for you!

01:15:42.650 --> 01:15:45.740
在那里躲着  我下班  一同走
Hide behind there. We'll go back together when I'm done.

01:15:46.160 --> 01:15:47.730
别让别人看到你
Don't let anyone see you!

01:15:48.120 --> 01:15:49.610
这次可真够瞧的了
This sure is fun.

01:16:03.890 --> 01:16:04.750
都脱光了
Everything!

01:16:05.010 --> 01:16:07.170
全都脱光了  衣服挂在那儿
Take everything off! Hang it up there!

01:16:08.100 --> 01:16:10.180
洗完澡可以拿回去
You'll get it back after the shower.

01:16:11.230 --> 01:16:12.390
向前走
Forward!

01:16:14.520 --> 01:16:17.610
记住自己的号码  方便认回衣服
Remember your number to get your clothes back!

01:16:20.700 --> 01:16:22.900
妇女小孩一同洗澡
Women and children will shower together.

01:16:23.410 --> 01:16:24.900
有没有跌伤
Are you hurt?

01:16:36.550 --> 01:16:37.710
谢谢  Βartolomeo
Thanks, Βartolomeo.

01:16:37.840 --> 01:16:41.510
以后你要整天躲在这里
From now on, you have to hide here the whole day.

01:16:41.680 --> 01:16:43.890
被他们发现  我们就丧失资格啦
If they see us now it's over. We're disqualified.

01:16:44.690 --> 01:16:45.680
我要做什么
What do I have to do?

01:16:46.190 --> 01:16:48.260
你要留在这里  Vittorino  帮帮忙
You have to stay. Vittorino, help me out.

01:16:48.570 --> 01:16:50.690
你一定要整天躲在这里
You have to hide here all day.

01:16:50.900 --> 01:16:53.820
别让人见到  尤其呼喝的人
Don't let anyone see you, especially those mean guys who yell.

01:16:55.120 --> 01:16:56.360
记着
Remember.

01:16:56.450 --> 01:16:58.360
躲起来
Stay hidden!

01:16:58.660 --> 01:17:00.780
这是游戏最难的部分了  如果玩得对...
This is the hardest part. If we get this right,

01:17:01.500 --> 01:17:05.540
每天得120分  一定赢到坦克
the tank is ours. It's worth 120 points a day.

01:17:06.210 --> 01:17:08.880
我会带你走  我会藏着你  大家都以为你失踪了
I'll take you with me. I'll hide you. You're gone.

01:17:09.340 --> 01:17:11.920
以前谁见过你  你是谁  他在哪儿
Who's ever seen you before? Who are you? Where is he?

01:17:12.220 --> 01:17:13.330
明白吗
Got it?

01:17:18.890 --> 01:17:20.090
明白了
Got ya!

01:17:22.020 --> 01:17:22.560
乖孩子
Good boy!

01:18:39.990 --> 01:18:42.370
有没有人  我有没有打扰到你们
Anybody here? Am l disturbing?

01:18:50.760 --> 01:18:52.830
过来
Come here!

01:18:53.260 --> 01:18:54.920
我们要尽快
Quick as lightning!

01:19:01.270 --> 01:19:02.520
早安  公主
Good morning, Princess!

01:19:03.310 --> 01:19:04.510
昨晚...
Last night,

01:19:04.610 --> 01:19:07.060
我整晚梦到你
I dreamt about you all night!

01:19:07.490 --> 01:19:11.070
我们去看电影
We were going to the movies.

01:19:11.320 --> 01:19:12.570
你穿着我喜欢的那套粉红套装
You were wearing that pink suit that I really like.

01:19:13.160 --> 01:19:15.240
我脑中只有你  公主
You're all I think about, Princess.

01:19:15.620 --> 01:19:18.160
惦念的只是你
I always think about you. And now...

01:19:18.460 --> 01:19:19.490
妈妈
Mommy!

01:19:19.840 --> 01:19:23.830
爸爸用轮车推我  但他不会推
Pop wheels me in the wheelbarrow, but he doesn't know how to drive!

01:19:24.050 --> 01:19:26.290
笑到我肚子痛
We laugh like crazy!

01:19:26.430 --> 01:19:29.100
我们领先呢  今天有得了多少分
We're in the lead! How many points do we have today?

01:19:29.600 --> 01:19:32.470
快跑  呼喝的坏蛋在我们后面
Run! The mean guys who yell are behind us!

01:19:32.680 --> 01:19:35.770
-哪里  -这里
- Where? - Over here! Come on!

01:19:49.620 --> 01:19:51.200
衣服干了没有
Are they dry?

01:19:52.120 --> 01:19:54.410
干了
They're dry.

01:19:54.670 --> 01:19:55.580
接住
Catch.

01:19:56.630 --> 01:19:57.830
穿上去
Get dressed.

01:20:12.320 --> 01:20:15.480
Vittorino  Alfonso等人呢
What happened to Vittorino, Alfonso and the others?

01:20:15.990 --> 01:20:17.610
他们活不成了
They didn't make it.

01:21:10.680 --> 01:21:12.720
一提起我  我就消失
"If you say my name, I'm not there anymore."

01:21:14.350 --> 01:21:15.300
沉默
Silence.

01:21:49.520 --> 01:21:51.480
谢天谢地  吓死我了  什么事
Thank goodness. I was getting scared. What happened to you?

01:21:51.860 --> 01:21:54.230
他们快疯了
They're half crazy!

01:21:56.030 --> 01:21:58.780
替我检查那军医...
The man who does the check-ups, the Captain;

01:21:58.910 --> 01:22:01.280
是我的朋友  我做侍者时认识
he's a friend of mine. l met him when l was a waiter.

01:22:01.450 --> 01:22:05.450
他说  高官们和他们的妻子会举行晚宴
He said they're having a dinner with all the officials and their wives.

01:22:05.710 --> 01:22:08.620
问我想不想去捧盘
He asked me if I wanted to wait tables at the dinner.

01:22:09.670 --> 01:22:12.670
他或者有办法送我们出去
Maybe he wants to help me. He might get us out of here.

01:22:19.510 --> 01:22:21.550
你看到Joshua了吗
Have you seen Joshua?

01:22:21.980 --> 01:22:23.220
不知道  什么意思
What do you mean, no?

01:22:30.990 --> 01:22:33.110
你在干什么  过来
What are you doing? Come here!

01:22:33.370 --> 01:22:34.400
不
No.

01:22:35.030 --> 01:22:36.990
叫你过来呢
l told you to come.

01:22:37.700 --> 01:22:39.280
不  出来啊
No? Come on out!

01:22:40.420 --> 01:22:43.290
看  你全身都弄脏了
Come out! Look here. You're all dirty.

01:22:43.920 --> 01:22:45.160
你去了哪里
Where have you been?

01:22:46.550 --> 01:22:49.420
我刚才在打纸牌
I had to finish playing rummy.

01:22:50.050 --> 01:22:52.540
他们用我们做扣子  制肥皂
They make buttons and soap out of us.

01:22:55.480 --> 01:22:56.760
什么
What are you saying?

01:22:56.850 --> 01:22:58.850
他们把我们送入火炉烧死
They burn us all in the oven.

01:23:00.020 --> 01:23:00.800
谁告诉你的
Who told you that?

01:23:02.150 --> 01:23:04.310
有个人一边哭一边说...
A man was crying.

01:23:04.780 --> 01:23:07.450
他们用我们做扣子  制肥皂
He said they make buttons and soap out of us.

01:23:09.530 --> 01:23:11.780
你信了吗
You fell for that?

01:23:12.120 --> 01:23:13.370
又信了
Again?

01:23:14.540 --> 01:23:17.490
我还以为你是个精乖的小孩
I thought you were a sharp boy; cunning, intelligent.

01:23:17.840 --> 01:23:21.090
用人来做扣子  制肥皂  怎可能
Buttons and soap out of people? That'll be the day!

01:23:22.050 --> 01:23:23.710
你却相信
You believed that?

01:23:24.470 --> 01:23:29.260
想想看  我用Bartolomeo变的肥皂洗手…
Just imagine. Tomorrow morning, l wash my hands with Bartolomeo...

01:23:29.520 --> 01:23:30.890
真好用
a good scrub.

01:23:31.140 --> 01:23:32.640
然后  扣Francesco变的扣子吗
Then I'll button up with Francesco.

01:23:33.020 --> 01:23:34.430
有没有可能  你说
Darn it all!

01:23:35.230 --> 01:23:37.110
Giorgio不见了
Look! l just lost Giorgio!

01:23:37.530 --> 01:23:38.940
这颗纽扣像他吗
Does this look like a person?

01:23:39.950 --> 01:23:43.150
他们戏弄你  你却信以为真
Come on! They were teasing you! And you fell for it!

01:23:43.450 --> 01:23:45.570
他们还说了什么
What else did they tell you?

01:23:45.870 --> 01:23:47.610
说我们会被送入火炉
That we get cooked in the oven.

01:23:51.750 --> 01:23:53.580
活活烧死
They burn us up in the oven.

01:23:55.010 --> 01:24:00.600
你也信了  他们说你就信吗
You fell for that too! You just eat everything up!

01:24:00.680 --> 01:24:02.800
我听过用柴当燃料
I've heard of a wood oven...

01:24:03.020 --> 01:24:05.510
没听过用人当燃料
but I've never seen a man oven before.

01:24:05.940 --> 01:24:09.060
我是木头做的  抓这个律师去烧吧
"I'm made of wood!" "Take this lawyer!"

01:24:09.270 --> 01:24:12.230
律师太湿  烧不着
"This lawyer doesn't burn. He's not dry enough.

01:24:12.450 --> 01:24:14.150
只会冒烟
Look at that smoke!"

01:24:15.870 --> 01:24:18.160
钮扣  肥皂  烧人
Buttons, soap, we get burned in the oven.

01:24:18.490 --> 01:24:20.490
别开玩笑了
Let's be serious now.

01:24:20.750 --> 01:24:23.530
我明天还要玩布袋竞赛呢
I have a bag race with the bad guys tomorrow.

01:24:23.960 --> 01:24:26.370
我不玩了  要回家去
That's enough. I want to go home.

01:24:28.880 --> 01:24:30.080
现在回去吗
Now?

01:24:30.300 --> 01:24:31.170
现在回去
Right now.

01:24:31.800 --> 01:24:35.010
现在下着雨  你会淋出病的
It's raining now. You'll come down with a terrible fever!

01:24:35.220 --> 01:24:37.050
我不管  现在就走
I don't care. Let's go.

01:24:38.100 --> 01:24:40.180
好  你非要走的话...
All right. If you want to go...

01:24:40.520 --> 01:24:44.270
我们走  收拾行李
I'll get our stuff and we'll leave.

01:24:45.070 --> 01:24:46.230
我们可以走
We can leave?

01:24:46.530 --> 01:24:49.860
当然  他们可以逼人留下吗
Naturally. What do you think they do, force people to stay here?

01:24:50.410 --> 01:24:52.030
好难
That'll be the day.

01:24:52.290 --> 01:24:54.860
异想天开  我们说走就走
Wouldn't that be great? Let's go. We'll pack our bags...

01:24:55.250 --> 01:24:56.830
收拾好行李就走
and get out of here.

01:24:57.130 --> 01:25:00.490
可惜  我们在领先  却弃权
What a shame. We were in the lead. We're quitting. Off the list we go.

01:25:01.010 --> 01:25:05.220
那辆真坦克会被其他孩子赢去
Some other kid will win the real tank.

01:25:05.470 --> 01:25:07.630
已经没有其他孩子了  我是唯一的一个
There aren't any other kids. I'm the only one left.

01:25:08.060 --> 01:25:11.420
已经没有孩子了吗  这里多着呢
There aren't any more kids? It's chock-full of them here!

01:25:11.560 --> 01:25:12.970
在哪里
Where are they then?

01:25:13.440 --> 01:25:16.110
都在躲着  绝不露面
They're all hiding. Nobody's supposed to see them.

01:25:16.440 --> 01:25:19.860
-都在认真玩游戏  -我不明白
- This is a serious game! – I just don't get it.

01:25:20.070 --> 01:25:21.900
我们拿到了多少分
How many points do we have?

01:25:22.030 --> 01:25:24.270
差不多687分
Almost 687.

01:25:24.490 --> 01:25:26.570
告诉过你一千次了
I told you a thousand times.

01:25:27.250 --> 01:25:28.570
不过  既然要走就走吧
Let's go, though.

01:25:28.790 --> 01:25:31.460
-我们本来会赢的...  -我们会赢吗
- We're winning, but if you want-- - We're winning?

01:25:31.790 --> 01:25:33.950
我们在领先  早已经告诉你
We're first, l told you.

01:25:34.420 --> 01:25:36.540
但你要退出  只好退出
But we'll quit if you want.

01:25:36.970 --> 01:25:39.640
我昨天才看过积分表
I saw the chart yesterday. We'll go anyway, though.

01:25:40.300 --> 01:25:42.210
拜拜  Bartolomeo  我和Joshua要走了
Bye, Bartolomeo. Joshua and I are leaving.

01:25:42.470 --> 01:25:44.050
我们讨厌这地方
We're fed up here.

01:25:44.140 --> 01:25:47.970
坦克已经造成
The tank is done. It's ready.

01:25:48.440 --> 01:25:51.390
抹干净火嘴再开车
Clean the spark plugs off before you start it.

01:25:51.650 --> 01:25:54.220
记得要拉开油门
Open the throttle...

01:25:54.530 --> 01:25:57.950
否则大炮会卡住轮带
otherwise the cannon will get stuck with the tracks.

01:25:58.200 --> 01:26:00.440
还有那支机枪  多么精致
And the gun. Did you see how nice it is? It came out beautiful!

01:26:00.660 --> 01:26:03.240
开车前记得松刹闸
Lift the emergency brake off before you move!

01:26:03.710 --> 01:26:06.460
我和他要走了
We're going.

01:26:06.670 --> 01:26:08.250
Joshua要退出
Joshua wants to quit.

01:26:08.380 --> 01:26:09.490
本来要开着坦克走的
We could have gone back with a tank soon,

01:26:09.660 --> 01:26:10.950
现在却要坐巴士
but we'll take the bus today.

01:26:11.340 --> 01:26:14.090
我和Joshua要走了  大家再见
Joshua and l are leaving. So long, everybody!

01:26:14.300 --> 01:26:16.050
我们讨厌这地方
We're tired of this place.

01:26:16.640 --> 01:26:19.310
走吧  否则赶不上巴士了
Let's go or we'll miss the bus.

01:26:24.320 --> 01:26:25.600
走吧  Joshua
Let's go, Joshua.

01:26:29.360 --> 01:26:32.150
我怕被雨淋湿  发高烧
It's raining. I'll come down with a terrible fever!

01:27:41.580 --> 01:27:45.490
是我  爸爸呀
It's me, Pop!

01:27:46.290 --> 01:27:49.040
我有重要的话跟你说
I have to tell you something important! Come here!

01:27:49.250 --> 01:27:51.710
那小鬼头今早一直躲避我
That little rascal's been running away all morning.

01:27:51.840 --> 01:27:54.510
-真的有小孩  -二千个
- Is there really a kid? - There must be two thousand!

01:27:54.800 --> 01:27:56.760
他们像小老鼠  到处躲
They're like mice. They hide all over the place!

01:27:57.010 --> 01:27:59.260
都想得到我们的坦克  停
Those creeps want our tank! Stop!

01:28:00.020 --> 01:28:01.130
等一等
Wait.

01:28:03.190 --> 01:28:04.730
我似乎见过他
I might have spotted him.

01:28:04.980 --> 01:28:06.890
他可能在附近
I think he's nearby.

01:28:07.150 --> 01:28:11.610
不如你去查一查  我在这里等
Look. Go see if he's hiding in there. I'll wait here.

01:28:11.860 --> 01:28:13.490
替你把风
I'll keep a watch out.

01:28:20.460 --> 01:28:21.570
他在那里  爸爸
He's there, Pop!

01:28:21.790 --> 01:28:23.620
-什么样子的  金发吗  -嗯
- What'd he look like? Blond? - Yes.

01:28:24.590 --> 01:28:26.790
正是他  他叫Schwanz
That's him then. His name is... Schwanz.

01:28:27.090 --> 01:28:29.050
躲在里面已经三个星期了
He's been in there for three weeks.

01:28:29.510 --> 01:28:31.590
他排第二  但我们领先
He was the runner up. We beat him, though!

01:28:32.140 --> 01:28:35.060
迟早我会找到其他的孩子
Sooner or later, I'll find the others too.

01:28:35.060 --> 01:28:37.430
-有多少个  -密密麻麻
- How many are there? - It's swarming, l told you.

01:28:37.770 --> 01:28:39.400
都躲着
They're all hidden.

01:28:48.950 --> 01:28:50.450
爸爸  看呀
Look, Pop!

01:28:50.620 --> 01:28:52.080
这是个匿藏点
There's a hideout!

01:28:53.460 --> 01:28:56.130
你  你  你  取消资格  我们走
Got ya, got ya, got ya! You're out! Let's go.

01:29:03.300 --> 01:29:05.050
靠  她看见我们了
Holy smokes! She saw us!

01:29:05.220 --> 01:29:06.680
我们被淘汰了吗
Are we out?

01:29:07.270 --> 01:29:09.220
她过来是因为她看见了你
She's coming over for you.

01:29:09.350 --> 01:29:11.510
现在玩沉默游戏
Now it's time for the "be quiet" game.

01:29:11.860 --> 01:29:13.730
你绝对不要吱声
You're never to speak.

01:29:14.320 --> 01:29:15.430
发誓
Swear it!

01:29:17.110 --> 01:29:18.820
-发誓啊  -我发誓
- Swear it! – I swear.

01:29:22.200 --> 01:29:24.690
他们咕噜咕噜  你反正听不懂
They all talk strange. You can't understand a word.

01:29:25.000 --> 01:29:27.400
我们过得这关  头奖就是我们的了
If we get through this, the first prize is ours.

01:29:27.830 --> 01:29:30.590
所有领先的人  都要玩沉默游戏
They're rounding up everyone in first place. It's the silence game.

01:29:30.960 --> 01:29:32.870
一声都不能出  知道吗
Not a word, got it?

01:29:39.850 --> 01:29:41.510
你为什么跟小孩在这里
Why are you here with the children?

01:29:41.640 --> 01:29:44.130
不准你和孩子交谈
Quiet! You're never to speak.

01:29:45.440 --> 01:29:46.600
我发誓不会
I swear.

01:30:42.590 --> 01:30:45.430
我有话对你说  很重要
I have to talk to you. Very important.

01:30:45.550 --> 01:30:48.390
-哪里  几时  -我会打暗号  过会儿
- Where? When? – I'll signal you. Later.

01:31:01.990 --> 01:31:03.020
谢谢
Thank you.

01:31:49.300 --> 01:31:52.170
我叫过你别跟小孩说话
I told you not to talk to the children.

01:32:20.130 --> 01:32:23.210
医生  内子也在这里
Doctor, my wife is here too.

01:32:45.410 --> 01:32:47.150
慢慢吃
Slowly.

01:32:47.450 --> 01:32:49.200
吃得太快不好
Eat slowly. It's bad for you.

01:32:49.410 --> 01:32:52.700
我们领先  可能早走
We're in the lead. We just might leave early.

01:32:52.840 --> 01:32:54.580
游戏提早结束
The game finishes early.

01:32:56.050 --> 01:32:58.800
我们要分外小心  不要出错
Don't make a mistake now that we're in the lead.

01:32:59.140 --> 01:33:00.210
慢慢吃
Slowly.

01:33:22.910 --> 01:33:24.740
留心听这个谜
So. Pay attention.

01:33:30.380 --> 01:33:33.090
肥肥丑丑
"Fat, fat, ugly, ugly,

01:33:33.260 --> 01:33:34.370
胆小到发黄
all yellow in reality.

01:33:36.180 --> 01:33:38.300
你问我  我是什么家伙
If you ask me what I am...

01:33:38.560 --> 01:33:40.600
我会答  贱贱贱
I answer, 'Cheep, cheep, cheep.'

01:33:46.860 --> 01:33:49.610
我一面走路  一面拉弓
Walking along l go, 'Poopoo'.

01:33:50.240 --> 01:33:52.730
我到底是谁
Who am I? Tell me true."

01:33:57.290 --> 01:33:59.370
小鸭  对吗
A duckling, right?

01:34:02.460 --> 01:34:04.340
是不是小鸭
Is it a duckling?

01:34:05.760 --> 01:34:08.080
不是
It's not!

01:34:09.560 --> 01:34:12.090
在维也纳的时候爸爸的一个兽医朋友出的这个谜面
A veterinarian friend of mine sent it to me from Vienna.

01:34:12.930 --> 01:34:14.970
我猜不出来
I can't send him mine...

01:34:15.400 --> 01:34:18.150
就不能还他一个谜面
until I solve this one.

01:34:19.400 --> 01:34:20.730
我以为是...
I thought...

01:34:21.150 --> 01:34:23.150
鸭嘴兽
duck-billed platypus...

01:34:23.570 --> 01:34:25.200
但鸭嘴兽不叫  贱贱贱
but it doesn't go, "Cheep, cheep, cheep."

01:34:25.450 --> 01:34:27.490
鸭嘴兽叫...
A duck-billed platypus goes...

01:34:33.840 --> 01:34:36.790
昨晚我替你翻译成意大利话
I translated it into Italian for you last night.

01:34:39.340 --> 01:34:41.750
你认为怎样
Well, what do you say?

01:34:43.510 --> 01:34:45.470
除了小鸭  我想不出什么
Everything points to a duckling.

01:34:48.230 --> 01:34:49.640
帮帮忙
Help me.

01:34:53.690 --> 01:34:55.650
求求你
For heaven's sake...

01:34:56.030 --> 01:34:57.190
帮帮忙
help me.

01:34:58.410 --> 01:35:00.730
我连睡也睡不着
I can't even sleep.

01:35:16.640 --> 01:35:18.960
谜底是小鸭
It's the duckling!

01:37:45.070 --> 01:37:48.240
过来
Come here!

01:37:49.280 --> 01:37:52.820
-我好累  -过来
- I'm tired. - Come here.

01:37:57.840 --> 01:37:59.380
我们在哪里
Where are we here?

01:38:00.010 --> 01:38:02.410
我可能走错了路
I might have taken the wrong way.

01:38:03.090 --> 01:38:05.500
乖孩子  睡吧  做个美梦
Good boy, sleep. Dream sweet dreams.

01:38:06.390 --> 01:38:07.970
可能现在就是个梦
Maybe it's only a dream!

01:38:08.680 --> 01:38:10.220
我们在做梦  Joshua
We're dreaming, Joshua.

01:38:10.810 --> 01:38:13.180
明早  妈妈会摇醒我们
Tomorrow morning, Mommy will come wake us up...

01:38:13.770 --> 01:38:16.940
端来牛奶  饼干
and bring us two nice cups of milk and cookies.

01:38:18.070 --> 01:38:19.530
我们先吃
First, we'll eat.

01:38:20.030 --> 01:38:22.780
然后我跟她做两三次爱
Then I'll make love to her two or three times...

01:38:23.530 --> 01:38:25.690
如果我还有气力
if I can.

01:39:14.350 --> 01:39:16.220
对不起  Bartolomeo
Excuse me, Bartolomeo.

01:39:17.180 --> 01:39:20.850
有两军官没有报到  我觉得他们溜掉了
They've called those two officers 20 times. l bet they escaped.

01:39:21.230 --> 01:39:22.430
你还听懂什么
Did you understand anything else?

01:39:22.690 --> 01:39:24.270
即使猜也猜得七七八八
It's clear enough.

01:39:24.780 --> 01:39:27.350
快打完仗  纳粹党树倒猢狲散
The war is over. They're running all over the place.

01:39:27.860 --> 01:39:29.610
货车要开到哪里
Where are those trucks going?

01:39:29.990 --> 01:39:32.450
最要紧的是别坐上去
The important thing is not to get on those trucks.

01:39:32.990 --> 01:39:34.540
满车去  空车回
They leave full and come back empty.

01:39:34.910 --> 01:39:36.320
你知道车子开到哪里吗
You know where they're going?

01:39:37.830 --> 01:39:40.670
女人呢  她们怎么了
What about the women? What's going on?

01:39:41.000 --> 01:39:43.460
我们离开这地狱吧  各散东西
Let's get out of this dump and split up.

01:39:44.130 --> 01:39:45.510
连行李也不用收拾
We don't even have to pack our bags!

01:39:46.050 --> 01:39:48.510
枪声  狗吠  吵了好几个钟头
I've been hearing only dogs and machine guns.

01:39:48.930 --> 01:39:50.760
他们想毁灭一切
They want to get rid of everything.

01:39:51.020 --> 01:39:52.220
我要走了
I'm leaving.

01:39:52.690 --> 01:39:55.010
我们在Viareggio再见  合作开铁砧厂
See you in Viareggio. We'll start an anvil factory!

01:39:55.310 --> 01:39:56.940
再见了  各位  我走了
So long, guys. I'm leaving.

01:40:14.380 --> 01:40:16.340
来看吧
Come see.

01:40:16.840 --> 01:40:19.210
他们多生气  气得在跳
Look how mad they are! Furious!

01:40:19.930 --> 01:40:22.760
看见了吗  都在找你
You see? They're looking for you.

01:40:23.270 --> 01:40:25.260
这样大阵仗  只为了找你
Just for you. All this is over you!

01:40:25.600 --> 01:40:27.760
你是最后一个  只剩下你
You're the last one! The last one to find!

01:40:28.150 --> 01:40:30.020
他们拼命找  连石头也翻起来
They're even looking under the rocks!

01:40:30.230 --> 01:40:33.230
游戏明早结束  举行颁奖典礼
The game is over tomorrow. They'll give the award.

01:40:33.690 --> 01:40:36.900
你躲得过今晚  就得到60分
If they don't find you tonight, it's worth 60 points!

01:40:37.160 --> 01:40:38.570
我们现在有几分
How many points do we have?

01:40:39.330 --> 01:40:41.950
我们有940分  再加60呢
We've got 940 points. Plus 60?

01:40:42.250 --> 01:40:43.740
-一千  -冠军  我们胜出
- A thousand! - First place! We win!

01:40:44.120 --> 01:40:47.040
他们找遍每个角落也找不到你
They're looking all over for you.

01:40:47.500 --> 01:40:50.080
今晚是最后一关  不要出错
No mistakes tonight. This is it!

01:40:50.550 --> 01:40:52.750
-快躲在箱内   -Schwanz在里面
- Go hide in that box, quick! - Schwanz is in there.

01:40:53.090 --> 01:40:54.260
谁
Who?

01:40:55.300 --> 01:40:57.930
那个金发男孩
The blond boy.

01:40:58.680 --> 01:41:01.970
他们昨天发现他  淘汰了
They got him yesterday. He was eliminated.

01:41:02.270 --> 01:41:04.940
那处最安全  谁也不会再去找
It's the safest place to hide. Nobody will look.

01:41:05.150 --> 01:41:08.100
走吧  快走
Let's go, quick as lightning. Come on!

01:41:08.820 --> 01:41:10.400
进去
Inside!

01:41:11.990 --> 01:41:15.190
带张毯  保暖
Take this blanket in case you get cold.

01:41:16.160 --> 01:41:18.620
我很快回来
I'll be back soon.

01:41:18.920 --> 01:41:22.330
我引开他们...  他在那边
I'll put them on the wrong track. I think I saw him over there!

01:41:51.960 --> 01:41:53.830
爸爸  我被你吓死啦
Pop, you scared me to death!

01:41:54.090 --> 01:41:56.960
那张毯给我  你冷吗
Give me the blanket. Are you cold?

01:41:57.710 --> 01:41:59.090
把外衣也给我
Give me your sweater then.

01:41:59.590 --> 01:42:02.170
我扔在树上  引开他们
I'll throw it on a tree and put them off track.

01:42:02.550 --> 01:42:03.880
他们到处找你
They're looking all over for you!

01:42:04.180 --> 01:42:08.100
大家都大喊  Joshua呢
Everybody's yelling, "Where's Joshua?"

01:42:08.270 --> 01:42:10.840
破口大骂  来势汹汹
They're even cursing. They're really, really mad!

01:42:11.270 --> 01:42:15.100
谁也不会找到你  我迟点回来
No one will find you. Bye, now. I'll be back later.

01:42:16.740 --> 01:42:17.730
听着
Listen...

01:42:18.160 --> 01:42:20.730
即使我很久才回来
if I'm really late coming back...

01:42:21.030 --> 01:42:22.830
你也不要动
don't you move.

01:42:23.290 --> 01:42:25.830
不要出来
Don't come out. You're not to come out...

01:42:26.170 --> 01:42:27.490
直到一点声  一个人都没有
until it's completely quiet...

01:42:29.840 --> 01:42:32.620
安全至上
and nobody is in sight, just to be safe.

01:42:32.880 --> 01:42:33.660
说一遍
Say it!

01:42:34.220 --> 01:42:37.170
我不出来  直到一个人都没有
I won't come out until nobody is around.

01:42:37.890 --> 01:42:39.430
乖孩子  小顽固
Good boy, stubborn.

01:43:08.760 --> 01:43:09.630
走开
Leave!

01:43:10.470 --> 01:43:12.340
走开  狗
Go away, dog!

01:43:13.060 --> 01:43:13.970
走开  你这只狗
Go, dog!

01:43:14.770 --> 01:43:22.310
走开
Leave.

