真的坦克
It's true!

01:50:43.280 --> 01:50:44.820
小朋友
Boy!

01:50:47.870 --> 01:50:50.700
你一个人吗  你叫什么
You alone? What’s your name?

01:50:53.000 --> 01:50:54.240
完全听不懂我的话吗
Can’t you understand at least a word of mine?

01:50:55.460 --> 01:50:56.660
来  我载你一程
Come on, I’ll give you a drive!

01:50:57.460 --> 01:50:58.410
上来
Come on in!

01:51:04.720 --> 01:51:10.930
