This is my story.

01:52:10.510 --> 01:52:12.670
这是我父亲所作的牺牲
This is the sacrifice my father made.

01:52:15.520 --> 01:52:17.640
这是我父亲赐我的恩典
This was his gift to me.

01:52:18.190 --> 01:52:19.600
我们赢了
We won!

01:52:19.690 --> 01:52:20.800
是的  我们赢了
Yes, we won!

01:52:22.980 --> 01:52:26.570
一千分  好开心啊
A thousand points to laugh like crazy about!

01:52:26.860 --> 01:52:30.030
我们得了冠军  坐坦克回家
We came in first! We're taking the tank home!

01:52:30.240 --> 01:52:33.030
我们赢了
We won!
